hadiths[527]{hadithnumber,text}:
4628,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ne Aadam (Alaihissalam) ko uski surat par takhleeq farmaya , unka qad saath haath tha, jab usney unhen paida kiya to farmaya : jaao us jamaat ko salam karo, us jamaat mein chand farishtey bethey huey they wo aap ko jo jawab den , wo ghor se sunen , chunanche wohi jawab tumhara aur tumhari aulad ka hoga, wo gaey aur unhoney un se kaha : Assalamualaikum ! unhoney kaha : Assalamualaikum-warahmatullah !'' unhoney unhen lafz Rahmatullah ka zayed jawab diya.'' farmaya : ''jannat mein janey wala her shakhs soorate Adam (Alaihissalam) par hoga, uska qad saath haath hoga, unke baad phir musalsal ab tak qad aur qaamat (kaanthi) mein kami waqey hoti chali aa rahi hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
4629,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke eik aadmi ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se daryaft kiya, kon sa (aadaab) Islam behtar hai? farmaya : ''(ye ke) tum khana khilaao aur tum jisey jantey ho usey bhi aur jisey nahin jantey usey bhi salam karo.'' muttafaq aleh."
4630,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''momin ke momin par chhe haq hain : jab wo bimar ho jaey to uski iyaadat karey, jab wo faut ho jaey to uskey janaazey mein shareek ho, jab wo dawat dey to usey qubul karey, jab wo us se mulaqat karey to usey salam karey, jab usey chheenk aaye (aur الحمد للہ kahe) to wo usey یرحمک اللہ keh kar jawab dey, aur uski mojudgi aur ghair mojudgi mein us se khair-khaahi karey.'' rawahu Nasai aur Tirmizi. sahibe Mishkat kehtey hain : aur maine isey na to saheehain mein paya hai na kitabul Humedi mein, lekin Jaame ul-usool ke writer (ibne Aseer) ne isey Nasai ki riwayat se zikr kiya hai."
4631,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum us waqt tak jannat mein dakhil nahin ho saktey jab tak tum momin nahin bin jatey , tum us waqt tak momin nahin bin saktey jab tak tum baham (aapas mein) mohabbat nahin kartey , kya main tumhen aisi chiz na bataaun ! jab tum usey karney lag jaaogey to tumhari baham (aapas mein) mohabbat ho jaey, aapas mein salam phailaao.'' rawahu Muslim."
4632,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''sawar , pedal chalney waley ko , pedal chalney wala bethey huey ko aur qaleel (kam), Kasir (ziyada) ko salam keren.'' muttafaq aleh."
4633,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''chhota badey ko , chalney wala bethey huey ko aur qaleel (kam), Kasir (ziyada) ko salam keren.'' Bukhari."
4634,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) bachchon ke paas se guzrey aur unhen salam kiya. muttafaq aleh.
4635,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''yahood aur Nasara ko salam karney mein pehal na karo, aur jab tum un mein se kisi ko raastey mein milo to unhen raastey ke eik taraf chalney par majbur kar do.'' rawahu Muslim."
4636,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab Yahudi tumhen salam kartey hain to un mein se eik tumhen yehi kehta hai : السام علیک (tum par maut waqey ho) lihaza tum unhen ye jawab do : wa-alaik (tum par bhi ho).'' muttafaq aleh."
4637,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab ehle-kitab tumhen salam karen to tum (jawab mein itna) kaho : '' wa'alaikum.'' muttafaq aleh."
4638,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, yahudiyon ki eik jamaat ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se ijazat talab ki to unhoney kaha : tum par maut waqey ho, maine kaha : balke tum par maut aur lanat waqey ho, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Aaisha ! be-shak Allah meharban hai wo her mamley mein meharbani aur narmi karney ko pasand farmata hai.'' maine arz kiya, kya aapney nahin suna ke unhoney kya kaha? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''maine keh diya tha : aur tum par (maut waqey ho) aur eik dusri riwayat mein : ''tum par '' ke alfaz hain. unhoney واؤ ka zikr nahin kiya. aur Bukhari ki riwayat mein hai : Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne farmaya : ''yahudi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aaye aur unhoney kaha : tum par maut waqey ho. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aur tum par.'' Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne farmaya : tum par maut waqey ho, Allah tum par lanat farmaai aur tum par naraz ho. (ye sun kar) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Aaisha ! thehro, narmi ikhtiyar karo, sakhti aur badgoi se ijtinab (bacha) karo.'' unhoney arz kiya : kya aapney nahin suna jo unhoney kaha? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya tum ne nahin suna jo maine kaha, maine unhen jawab dey diya tha, unke mutalliq meri badduaa qubul ho gaee jabkey unki merey mutalliq badduaa qubul nahin hui.'' aur Muslim ki riwayat mein hai : aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aap badgoi karney wali na banen, kyonkey Allah be takalluf aur baa-takalluf badgoi ko pasand nahin farmata.'' muttafaq aleh."
4639,"Hazrat Usama bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka eik aisi majlis se guzar hua jis mein musalman , buton ke pujaari mushrik aur Yahudi bethey huey they, to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen salam kiya. muttafaq aleh."
4640,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''raaston mein bethney se ijtinab (bacha) karo.'' Sahaba ne arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! wahan bethna hamari majburi hai uskey baghair guzaara nahin, ham wahan beth kar baaten kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar tum ne zarur bethna hi hai to phir raastey ka haq ada karo.'' unhoney arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! raastey ka haq kya hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''nazren jhukaanaa, takleef na pahunchana, salam ka jawab dena, neki ka hukm dena aur burai se mana karna.'' muttafaq aleh."
4641,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se us (hadees saabiq mein mazkura) qissey ke mutalliq riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aur raasta batana.'' Imam Abu-Dawood ne Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hadees ke baad isi tarah riwayat kiya hai. rawahu Abu-Dawood."
4642,"Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se us qisse ke barey mein riwayat kartey hain, farmaya : ''mazloom ki madad karo aur raasta bhatkey huey shakhs ki rehnumai karo.'' Imam Abu-Dawood ne Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees ke baad isi tarah riwayat kiya hai, aur maine , un dono hadeeson ko Saheehain mein nahin paya. rawahu Abu-Dawood."
4643,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''musalman ke musalman par dastoor ke mutabiq chhe huquq hain : jab us se mulaqat karey to usey salam karey, jab wo dawat dey to usey qubul karey, jab wo chheenk maarey (aur wo Alhamdu-lillah kahe) to usey Yarhamkallah kahe, jab wo bimar ho jaey to uski iyaadat karey, jab wo faut ho jaey to uskey janaazey mein shareek ho, aur uskey liye wohi kuchh pasand karey jo wo apney liye pasand karta hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi aur Darmi."
4644,"Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke eik aadmi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaya aur usney kaha : Assalamualaikum ! aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey jawab diya, phir wo beth gaya to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''(uskey liye) das (nekiyan) hain.'' phir doosra shakhs aaya aur usney kaha : Assalamualaikum Wa Rahamtullah ! aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey jawab diya, jab wo beth gaya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''(uskey liye) bees (nekiyan) hain.'' phir eik aur shakhs aaya aur usney kaha : Assalamualaikum Wa Rahamtullah Wa Barkaatuh ! aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey jawab diya, jab wo beth gaya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''(uskey liye) tees (nekiyan) hain.'' rawahu Tirmizi aur Abu-Dawood."
4645,"Hazrat Muaz bin Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se usi mafhoom ki hadees naqal kartey huey ye izafa naqal kya hai, phir eik aur aaya aur usney kaha : Assalamualaikum w rahmatullah w barkaatuh w maghfiratuh! aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' ( uskey liye ( chaalis ( nekiyan ( hain.'' aur farmaya : '' fazaail isi tarah hotey hain.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
4646,"Hazrat abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' salam mein pehal karney wala shakhs Allah ka sab se ziyada qaribi hai.'' rawahu Ahmed w Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood ."
4647,Hazrat Jarir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) khawatin ke paas se guzrey to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen salam kya. rawahu Ahmed .
4648,"Hazrat Ali bin abi Talib (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab logon ki jamaat ka guzar ho to unki taraf se eik aadmi ka salam karna kafi hai aur jo bethey huey hain unki taraf se eik aadmi ka jawab dena kafi hai.'' Behaqi ne Shobil-emaan mein usey marfoo riwayat kya hai. aur Abu-Dawood ne is hadees ko riwayat karney ke baad kaha : Hasan bin Ali ne usey marfoo riwayat kya hai, aur wo Abu-Dawood ke ustaad hain. ( rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan w Abu-Dawood ( ."
4649,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib apney walid se aur wo apney dada se riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : jisney hamarey ilawa kisi aur se mushaabihat ikhtiyar ki wo ham mein se nahin, tum yahood w Nasara se mushaabihat ikhtiyar na karo, kyonkey yahudiyon ka salam ungliyon ke sath ishara karna hai jabkey esaiyon ka salam hatheliyon ke sath ishara karna hai.'' Tirmizi, aur unhoney kaha : iski sanad zaeef hai. rawahu Tirmizi ."
4650,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi apney ( musalman ( bhai se miley to usey salam karey, agar un dono ke darmiyan koi darkht ya deewar ya koi pathar haael ho jaey phir us se mulaqat ho jaey to chahiye ke usey salam karey.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
4651,"Hazrat Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum kisi ghar mein jaao to wahan ke rehney walon ko salam karo aur jab tum ( wahan sey) niklo to us ghar walon ko widaai salam kaho .'' Behaqi ne usey Shobil-emaan mein mursal riwayat kya hai. ( rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( ."
4652,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''beta! jab tum apney ghar walon ke paas jaao to salam karo, (us tarah ( tum par aur terey ehle khana par barkat hogi .'' rawahu Tirmizi ."
4653,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''pehley salam phir kalam.'' Tirmizi, aur unhoney farmaya : ye hadees munkar hai. rawahu Tirmizi ."
4654,"Hazrat Imran bin hisn (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham daure-jahiliyat mein (b-waqt mulaqat) kaha kartey they : Allah teri aankh thandi rakhey aur tum tar-o-taza w khush w khurram haalat mein subh karo. jab Islam aaya to hamen us se rok diya gaya. rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
4655,"Hazrat ghalib bayan kartey hain, ham Hasan Basri (Raziallahu anhu) ke darwazey par bethey they ke eik aadmi aaya aur usney kaha : merey walid ne merey dada se riwayat kya, unhoney kaha, merey walid ne mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein bheja : aap ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar unhen salam arz karna , unhoney kaha : main aap ki khidmat mein pahuncha aur maine arz kya ke merey walid aap ko salam arz kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum par aur tumharey walid par salam ho.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
4656,"Hazrat abul-Ala bin hizrami se riwayat hai ke Ala hizrami (Raziallahu anhu) , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke) muqarrar karda Behreen ke) hukmran they, aur jab wo aap ki taraf khat likhtey to apney naam ( az taraf Ala ( se shuru kya kartey they. rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
4657,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi khat likhey to wo usey khaak aalud kar dey kyonkey is tarah karney se kaam jald w aasan ho jata hai.'' Tirmizi, aur farmaya : ye hadees munkar hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
4658,"Hazrat Zaid bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke samney kaatib tha, maine aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''qalam apni kaan par rakho kyonkey aisa karna ( kaan par qalam rakhna ( maqsad w anjam jald yad kara deta hai.'' Tirmizi, aur unhoney farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai aur iski sanad mein zauf hai. rawahu Tirmizi ."
4659,"Hazrat Zaid bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey hukm farmaya ke main suryani zaban seekhun. eik dusri riwayat mein hai ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya ke main yahudiyon ki kitaabat seekhoon aur farmaya : ''mujhey yahood ki kitaabat ka andesha hai.'' Zaid bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : maine nisf maah se pehley hi unki zaban seekh li, jab aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) yahood ke naam khat likhtey to main tehreer karta aur jab wo aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke naam khat likhtey to unke maktoob mein aap ko padh kar sunata tha. rawahu Tirmizi ."
4660,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi kisi majlis mein aaye to wo salam karey, phir agar wo bethna chahey to beth jaey, aur jab wo wahan se uthey to wo salam karey, pehla (salam) doosrey ( salam ( se ziyada haq nahin rakhta .'' rawahu Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood ."
4661,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' raaston mein bethney mein koi khair w bhalai nahin, magar us shakhs ke liye ( khair ( hai jo raasta bataey, salam ka jawab dey , nazar jhukaey aur jo sawari par bojh rakhwaaney mein madad karey.'' aur abu jarii se marwi (bayan) hadees ( '' baab Fazal sadqa'' ( mein zikr ki gaee hai. ( rawahu fi Sharahus-sunnah ( ."
4662,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab Allah ne Adam (Alaihissalam) ko paida farmaya aur un mein rooh phunki to unhoney chheenk maari aur Alhamdulillah kaha, unhoney Allah ki tofiq se uski hamd bayan ki, to unke rab ne unhen kaha : Allah tujh par rehem karey, Adam ! farishton ki us jamaat ki taraf jaao jo bethi hui hai, (wahan ja kar) kaho : Assalamualaikum ! unhoney kaha : Assalamualaikum ! unhoney kaha : Assalamualaikum Wa Rahmatullah ! phir wo wahan se apney rab ke paas wapis aaye to usney farmaya : ''be-shak ye tumhara aur teri aulad ka bahami (aapsi) salam hai. Allah ne unhen hukm diya jabkey uskey dono haath band they, tum dono mein se jisey chaho ikhtiyar kar lo, unhoney kaha : maine apney rab ka daayan haath muntakhab (chun) kar liya jabkey merey rab ke dono haath daain ba-barkat hain, phir Allah Taala ne apney daain haath ko phelaya to is mein Adam (Alaihissalam) aur unki aulad thi, unhoney arz kiya, rab ji ! ye kon hain? farmaya : ye tumhari aulad hai, her insan ki umr uski dono aakhon ke darmiyan likhi hui thi, aur un main eik aisa aadmi tha jo un sab se ziyada roshan (chehrey wala) tha, unhoney arz kiya, rab ji ! ye kon hai? farmaya : ye aap ke bete Dawud (Alaihissalam) hain, aur maine unki umr chaalis saal likhi hai, unhoney arz kiya : rab ji ! uski umr mein izafa farma , Allah Taala ne farmaya : bas yehi hai jo maine uskey liye likh di hai, unhoney arz kiya, rab ji ! maine apni umr se saath saal usey ata kar diye , Allah Taala ne farmaya : ye tera maamla hai, farmaya : phir wo jis qadr Allah ne chaha jannat mein rahey, phir wahan se utaar diye gaey, aur Adam (Alaihissalam) apni umr shumar kiya kartey they, jab maut ka farishta unke paas aaya to unhoney farmaya : tum jaldi aagey ho kyonkey meri umr to hazar baras likhi gaee thi, usney arz kiya, ji haan , (durust hai) lekin aap (Alaihissalam) ne apney bete Dawud (Alaihissalam) ko saath saal dey diye they, unhoney inkar kiya isi wajeh se unki aulad ne bhi inkar kiya, aur wo bhool gaey isi wajeh se unki aulad bhi bhool jati hai.'' aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''usi din se likhney aur gawahi deney ka hukm farmaya gaya.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
4663,"Hazrat Asma binte Yazid (Raziallahu anhu) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamari khawatin ki jamaat ke paas se guzrey to aapney hamein salam kiya. rawahu Abu-Dawood, ibne-Maja aur Darmi."
4664,"Hazrat Tufail bin Ubai bin Kab se riwayat hai ke wo ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaya kartey they aur wo unke sath subah ke waqt baazar jatey , raawi bayan kartey hain, jab ham baazar jatey to Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) wahan maamuli karobar karney waley, badey sarmaya daar , miskeen aur jis kisi shakhs ke paas se bhi guzartey to usey salam kartey , Tufail bayan kartey hain, main eik roz Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaya to unhoney mujhey baazar janey ke liye kaha, maine unhen kaha : aap baazar mein kya karengey? jabkey aap kisi bai (saude) par rukte nahin, na sodey ke mutalliq daryaft kartey hain, na uski qeemat poochhtey hain aur na aap baazar ki majaalis mein bethtey hain, lihaza aap yahan hi tashrif rakhen aur ham baat cheet kartey hain, raawi bayan kartey hain, Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujhey farmaya : pet waley ! raawi bayan kartey hain, Tufail ka pet bada tha, ham salam ki gharz se jatey hain, ham her milney waley ko salam kartey hain. (rawahu Maalik aur al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan)."
4665,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, eik aadmi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aaya aur usney arz kiya, falan shakhs ka merey baagh mein khajoor ka eik darkht hai, wo us khajoor ke darkht ki wajeh se mujhey eza (takleef) pahunchata hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne pegham bheja ke apna khajoor ka darkht mujhey farokht kar do, usney kaha : nahin : aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''chalo mujhey hiba kar do.'' usney kaha : nahin, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jannat mein khajoor ke darkht ke badley mein mujhey farokht kar do.'' usney kaha : nahin, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''maine salam kehney mein bukhl (kanjusi) karney waley ke ilawa tujh se ziyada bakheel (kanjus) koi aur nahin dekha.'' (rawahu Ahmed aur al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan)."
4666,"Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' salam mein pehal karney wala takabbur se bari hota hai.'' (rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan)."
4667,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) hamarey paas aaye, unhoney kaha ke umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujhey apney paas bula bheja , main unke darwazey par aaya aur teen baar salam kiya, mujhey jawab na mila to main lot gaya, unhoney (mujh sey) puchha : tumhen kis chiz ne hamarey paas na aaney diya? maine kaha : main aaya tha aur aap ke darwazey par teen baar salam kiya tha lekin tum ne mujhey jawab na diya isliye main wapis chala gaya, kyonkey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey farmaya tha : ''jab tum mein se koi teen baar ijazat talab karey aur usey ijazat na miley to wo wapis chala jaey.'' umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : is par daleel pesh karo. Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : main unke sath khada hua aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas ja kar gawahi di. muttafaq aleh."
4668,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey farmaya : ''tumhara mujh se ijazat lena yehi hai ke tum parda uthaao aur tum meri poshida baaten sun lo (to aa jaao) jab tak main tujhey aisey karney se mana na kar dun.'' rawahu Muslim."
4669,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main apney walid ke zimme qarz ke mutalliq Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur maine darwaza khatkhataayaa to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kon hai?'' maine kaha : main, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main, main.'' goya aapney isey napasand farmaya. muttafaq aleh."
4670,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath aap ke ghar mein dakhil hua aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik piyale mein doodh paya to farmaya : ''Abu-Huraira ! eahle-suffa ke paas jaao, aur unhen merey paas bula laao.'' main unke paas gaya aur unhen bula laya, wo aaye aur (andar aaney ki) ijazat talab ki, aapney unhen ijazat de-di to wo andar aagey. Bukhari."
4671,"Hazrat Kalda bin Hanbal se riwayat hai ke Safwan bin Umayya (Raziallahu anhu) ne (merey haath) doodh ya hiran ka bachcha aur kakdi, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein bheji, jabkey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) baalai (upri) ilaqey mein they, raawi bayan kartey hain, main aap ke paas gaya to maine na salam kiya aur na ijazat talab ki, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''wapis jaao aur kaho : Assalamualaikum ! kya main aa sakta hun?'' rawahu Tirmizi aur Abu-Dawood."
4672,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se kisi ko bulaya jaey aur wo pegham laney waley ke sath hi aa jaey to ye uskey liye ijazat hi hai.'' aur unhi ki riwayat mein hai, farmaya : ''aadmi ka aadmi ki taraf qaasid bhejna uski ijazat hi hai.'' (Sahih) rawahu Abu-Dawood."
4673,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Basar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) kisi ke darwazey par tashrif latey to aap apna chehra darwazey ke samney na kartey , balke uskey daain koney ya baain koney par aatey to farmatey : ''Assalamualaikum ! Assalamualaikum !'' un dino darwazon par pardey nahin hotey they. rawahu Abu-Dawood. aur Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hadees : aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Assalamualaikum Rahmatullah'' (باب الضیافۃ) mein zikr ki gaee hai."
4674,"Hazrat Ata bin Yasar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke eik aadmi ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se masla daryaft kartey huey arz kiya : kya main apni maa (ke paas jatey waqt us) se ijazat talab karun? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''haan.'' us aadmi ne arz kiya, main ghar mein uskey sath hi rehta hun, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''phir bhi us se ijazat talab karo.'' us aadmi ne arz kiya : main uska khaadim hun, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''phir bhi ijazat talab karo, kya tum usey uriyaan (nangi) haalat mein dekhna pasand kartey ho?'' usney arz kiya : nahin, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''us se ijazat talab karo.'' Imam Maalik (Raziallahu anhu) ne isey mursal riwayat kiya hai. la risaala, (rawahu Maalik)."
4675,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas raat ke waqt aur din ke waqt janey ki ijazat thi, jab main raat ke waqt jata to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) merey liye (bator alamat ijazat) khans detey they. rawahu Nasai."
4676,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs (ijazat leney ki khatir) salam se ibtida na karey to usey ijazat na do.'' (rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan).
4677,"Hazrat Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha : kya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke Sahaba mein musaafe (par amal) tha? unhoney farmaya : haan. Bukhari."
4678,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Hasan bin Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ka bosa liya , us waqt Aqraa bin Habis (Raziallahu anhu) bhi aap ke paas they, Aqraa (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kiya : merey das bachchey hain, maine un mein se kisi ka bosa nahin liya , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne (tajjub sey) uski taraf dekha, phir farmaya : ''jo shakhs rehem nahin karta is par rehem nahin kiya jata.'' muttafaq aleh. aur ham Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hadees : ( أَثَمَّ لُکَعُ ( baab manaaqib ehale--bait Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) wa alaihim ajmaeen mein Insha Allah Taala zikr karengey. jabkey Umme-Hani (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hadees (baab-ul-amaan ( mein zikr ki gaee hai."
4679,"Hazrat Bara bin Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab do musalman mulaqat kartey waqt musaafa kartey hain, to unke alag honey se pehley unhen bakhsh diya jata hai.'' Ahmed, Tirmizi, ibne-Maja . aur Abu-Dawood ki riwayat mein hai, farmaya : ''jab do musalman mulaqat kartey waqt musaafa kartey hain, Allah ki hamd bayan kartey hain, aur us se maghfirat talab kartey hain, to unhen bakhsh diya jata hai.'' rawahu Ahmed, Tirmizi, ibne-Maja aur Abu-Dawood."
4680,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, kisi aadmi ne arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! ham mein se aadmi apney bhai ya apney dost se mulaqat karta hai, to kya wo uskey samney sar jhukaey? farmaya : ''nahin.'' usney kaha : kya wo usey galey lagaey aur uska bosa ley? farmaya : ''nahin.'' usney arz , kiya wo uska haath pakad kar us se musaafa karey? farmaya : ''haan.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
4681,"Hazrat abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' mareez ki iyaadat is tarah puri hoti hai ke tum mein se koi eik apna haath uski peshani par ya uskey haath par rakh kar us se daryaft karey : ''kya haal hai?'' aur tumhara aapas mein pura salam dua, musaafa karna hai.'' Ahmed, Tirmizi, aur Imam Tirmizi (Raziallahu anhu) ne usey zaeef qarar diya hai. rawahu Ahmed w Tirmizi ."
4682,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Zaid bin Harisa (Raziallahu anhu) Madina tashrif laye to us waqt Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) merey ghar mein tashrif farma they. wo aap ke paas aaye to unhoney darwaza khatkhataaya, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) (farte-mohabbat sey) apna kapda ghaseet-tey huye, qamis pehney baghair, uski taraf chaley, Allah ki qasam! maine us se pehley aur na uskey baad aap ko qamis ke baghair dekha, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey galey lagaya aur uska bosa liya. rawahu Tirmizi ."
4683,"Hazrat Ayub bin Bashir, anza qabiley ke eik aadmi se riwayat kartey hain ke usney kaha : maine Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha : kya jab tum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se mulaqat kartey they to wo tum se musaafa kya kartey they? unhoney farmaya : main jab bhi aap se mila hun, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujh se musaafa kya hai, aapney eik roz mujhey talab farmaya lekin main ghar par nahin tha, jab main aaya to mujhey bataya gaya, main aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aap us waqt chaarpai par tashrif farma they, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey galey lagaya, ye ( galey lagana ( bahut hi behtar tha, bahut hi behtar . rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
4684,"Hazrat Ikrima bin abi jahal (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jis roz main ( baiat Islam ke liye ( Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Muhajir sawar ke liye khush aamadeed .'' rawahu Tirmizi ."
4685,"Hazrat Usaid bin Huzair (Raziallahu anhu) la talluq ansaar ke eik qabiley se tha, wo bayan kartey hain : eik din wo logon se baaten kar rahey they aur wo mazah tabiat they aur wo unhen (apni baaton ke zariey) hansa rahey they, to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik lakdi se uskey pehlu par chob lagai, unhoney kaha : mujhey badla den, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main badla deta hun.'' unhoney arz kya : aap par to qamis hai jabkey mujh par qamis nahin, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne qamis uthai to main aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se chimat gaya aur aap ke pehlu ko bosa deney laga , aur arz kya : Allah ke Rasool ! main bas yehi chahta tha. rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
4686,"Hazrat Shobi (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Jaafar bin abi Talib (Raziallahu anhu) ka istaqbal kya to unhen galey lagaya aur unki aakhon ke darmiyan (peshani par) bosa diya. Abu-Dawud, Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan mursalan. jabkey masaabeh ke baaz nuskhon mein aur Sharahus-sunnah mein al-bayazi ki sanad se muttasil hai. ( rawahu Abu-Dawood w al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( ."
4687,"Hazrat Jaafar bin abi Talib (Raziallahu anhu) se sarzameene-Habsha se wapsi ke waqie ke barey mein marwi (bayan) hai, unhoney farmaya : jab ham Madina pahunchey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mera istaqbal kya aur mujhey galey laga liya, phir farmaya : ''main nahin janta ke mujhey Fateh khaibar ki ziyada khushi hai ya Jaafar ki aamad ki.'' ittifaq se unki aamad Fateh khaibar ke roz thi. (rawahu fi Sharahus-sunnah) ."
4688,Hazrat Zaare (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain aur wo wafad abdul-Qais mein shamil they : jab ham Madina pahunchey to ham apni sawaariyon se jaldi jaldi utrey aur ham ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke haath aur paaon ko bosa diya. rawahu Abu-Dawood.
4689,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki haiyet, seerat w soorat, eik riwayat mein hai : baat-cheet mein Fatima (Raziallahu anhu) se ziyada kisi ko mushabeh nahin paya, jab wo aatin to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) unka istaqbal kartey, aap unka haath pakadtey aur unka (peshani par) bosa letey aur unhen apni jagah par bithaatey, aur jab aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) unke paas tashrif ley jatey to wo bhi aap ka istaqbal kartin, aap ka haath pakadtin aur aapka bosa letin aur aap ko apni jagah par bithaatin. rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
4690,"Hazrat Bara (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, (kisi ghazwe se wapsi par) mein sab se pehley abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath Madina aaya to unki beti Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) leti hui thin aur wo bukhar mein mubtala thin, abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) unke paas aaye to farmaya : piyari beti! tumhara kya haal hai? aur unhoney unke rukhsaar par bosa diya. rawahu Abu-Dawood."
4691,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas eik bacha laya gaya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uska bosa liya aur farmaya : ''sun lo! ye (bachey) bukhl aur buzdili ka baais hotey hain, aur be-shak ye Allah Taala ki taraf se Atiya hain.'' ( rawahu fi Sharahus-sunnah) ."
4692,"Hazrat Yala (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Hasan aur Husain (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki taraf tezi se dodtey aaye to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne un dono ko galey laga liya, aur farmaya : ''be-shak aulad bukhl aur buzdili ka baais hoti hai.'' rawahu Ahmed ."
4693,"Hazrat Ata khuraasani (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''musaafa kya karo (us sey) keena jata rehta hai, hadiye (tohfey) diya karo, baham (aapas mein) mohabbat paida hogi aur dushmani w ranjish jati rahegi.'' Imam Malik ne usey mursal riwayat kya hai. rawahu Malik."
4694,"Hazrat Bara bin Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ne dopehar se pehley chaar rakaat (Namaze-chaasht) padhi, goya usney wo rakaat shabe-qadr mein ada kin, aur jab do musalman musaafa kartey hain, to unke sarey gunah gir jatey hain.'' ( rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( ."
4695,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab bano Qureza, Saad (Raziallahu anhu) ka faisla qubul karney par razi huey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne kisi ko unki taraf bheja, aur wo aap ke qarib hi they, chunanche wo eik gadhey par Sawar ho kar aaye, aur jab wo masjid ke qarib pahunchey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ansaar se farmaya : ''apney sardar ki taraf khadey ho jaao.'' muttafaq aleh. aur ye hadees mukammal taur par (baab hukm asraa) mein guzar chuki hai."
4696,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''koi aadmi kisi aadmi ko uski jagah se utha kar wahan mat bethey, balke wusat w kushadgi paida karo.'' muttafaq aleh."
4697,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs apni jagah se uthey aur wo phir wahin wapis aa jaey to us jagah ka wohi ziyada haqdaar hai.'' rawahu Muslim.
4698,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Sahaba kiram (Raziallahu anhu) ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se badh kar koi shakhs ziyada mehbub nahin tha, uskey bawajud jab wo aap ko dekhtey to wo khadey nahin hotey they, kyonkey wo jaantey they ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) usey napasand kartey hain. aur unhoney farmaya : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
4699,"Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ko ye pasand ho ke log uskey samney khadey rahen to wo apna thikana jahannam mein bana ley.'' rawahu Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood ."
4700,"Hazrat abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) lathi ka sahara lekar bahar tashrif laye to ham aap ki khatir khadey ho gaey, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum aisey na khadey hua karo jaisey ajmi log eik doosrey ki tazeem mein khadey hotey hain.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
4701,"Hazrat Saeed bin abul-Hasan (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) gawahi ke silsile mein hamarey paas aaye to eik aadmi unki khatir apni jagah se uth khada hua, unhoney wahan bethney se inkar kar diya aur farmaya ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usse mana farmaya hai, aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne us se bhi mana farmaya hai ke koi shakhs aisey aadmi ke kapdey se apna haath saaf karey jo usney usey nahin pehnaya. rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
4702,"Hazrat abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) beth jatey to ham aap ke ird-gird beth jatey they, phir aap khadey hotey aur aap ka wapis aaney ka irada hota to aap apna joota utaar kar ya apni koi chiz wahan rakh jatey jis se Sahaba samajh jatey (ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) wapis aaeyngey) aur wo wahin bethey rehtey. rawahu Abu-Dawood."
4703,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu), Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kisi aadmi ke liye jayez nahin ke wo do aadmiyon ke darmiyan, unki ijazat ke baghair alehdgi paida karey (aur khud un dono ke darmiyan beth jaey ).'' rawahu Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood ."
4704,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib apney walid se aur wo apney dada se riwayat kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum do aadmiyon ke darmiyan unki ijazat ke baghair mat betho.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
4705,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamarey sath masjid mein tashrif rakhtey aur hamarey sath guftgu farmaya kartey they, aur jab aap khadey hotey to ham der tak khadey rehtey yahan tak ke ham aapko dekhtey ke aap apni kisi zauja mohtarma ke ghar dakhil ho jatey. (rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan)."
4706,"Hazrat Waasila bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, eik aadmi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua, jabkey aap masjid mein tashrif farma they, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) uski khatir apni jagah se hat gaey to aadmi ne arz kya, Allah ke Rasool! jagah to kafi hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''be-shak musalman ka haq hai ke jab uska bhai usey dekhey to wo uskey liye (apni jagah se kuch ( hat jaey.'' Imam Behaqi ne dono ahadis Shobil-emaan mein zikr ki hain. (rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan) ."
4707,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko Kaba ke sehan mein apney haathon ke sath got maar kar bethey huey dekha. Bukhari ."
4708,"Hazrat Ubaada bin Tameem apney chacha se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko masjid mein chit letey huey dekha, aapney apna eik paaon doosrey par rakha hua tha. muttafaq aleh."
4709,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mana farmaya ke aadmi chit letey huey apna eik paaon utha kar doosrey par rakhey. rawahu Muslim ."
4710,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum mein se koi shakhs chit let kar apna eik paaon doosrey par na rakhey .'' rawahu Muslim .
4711,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' eik dafa eik aadmi soot pehney huey takabbur ke andaz mein chal raha tha aur uskey nafs ne usey ghurur mein dal rakha tha, usey zamin mein dhansa diya gaya, aur wo roze-qiyamat tak is mein utarta chala jaeyga.'' muttafaq aleh."
4712,"Hazrat Jabir bin Samra (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko baaeyn pehlu takiye par tek lagaey huey dekha . rawahu Tirmizi ."
4713,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) masjid mein bethtey to aap apney haathon se got maar letey they. rawahu rizeen."
4714,"Hazrat Qeela binte-Makhrima (Raziallahu anhu) bayan karti hain ke unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko masjid mein Qarfasa ke taur par bethey huey dekha, ( paaon par bethey huey they aur bazuon ko pindliyon ke gird lapet rakha tha), wo bayan karti hain, jab maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko , khaashe aur mutwaaze haalat mein dekha to khof ki wajeh se main laraz gaee. rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
4715,"Hazrat Jabir bin Samra (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Fajr ki Namaz padhtey to Suraj ke achi tarah tulu ho janey tak aalti-paalti maar kar (chaar zaanu ho kar) apni jagah par bethey rehtey . rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
4716,Hazrat abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) raat ke waqt padaaw daltey to aap apney daain pehlu par let-tey they aur jab subh se thoda sa pehley padaaw daltey to aap apni kohni khadi kartey aur hatheli par sar rakh letey they. ( rawahu fi Sharahus-sunnah) .
4717,Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ki aal se kisi shakhs ne bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka bistar bas usi qadr tha jis qadr kapdey mein maiyat ko qabr mein rakha jata hai aur masjid ( baaz ne kaha : jaey Namaz (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sar ke paas thi. rawahu Abu-Dawood .
4718,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik aadmi ko masjid mein pet ke bal letey huey dekha to farmaya : ''is tarah letney ko Allah pasand nahin farmata.'' rawahu Tirmizi ."
4719,"Hazrat Yaeesh bin Tikhfa bin Qais ghifaari apney walid se riwayat kartey hain, aur wo as-haabe-suffa mein se they, unhoney farmaya : main seeney ke dard ki wajeh se pet ke bal leta hua tha ke achcha eik aadmi apney paaon se mujhey hilaaney laga aur usney kaha : ''is tarah letney se Allah naraz hota hai.'' maine dekha to wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) they. rawahu Abu-Dawood w ibne-Maja."
4720,"Hazrat Ali bin Sheban (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs raat ke waqt ghar ki chhat par so jaey aur us (chhat) ke pardey na hon, aur eik riwayat mein hai is par pathar na hon to us se zimma uth gaya.'' Abu-Dawood"
4721,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mana farmaya ke aadmi kisi aisi chhat par soey jiskey pardey na hon. rawahu Tirmizi ."
4722,"Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jo shakhs majlis ke beech mein bethta hai wo Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki zaban par maloon hai. rawahu Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood ."
4723,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''behtareen majlis wo hai jo faraakh ho.''( jahan logon ko bethney mein tangi na ho ( rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
4724,"Hazrat Jabir bin Samra (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tashrif laye to aap ke Sahaba kiram (Raziallahu anhu) bethey huey they, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya wajeh hai ke main tumhen alag-alag ( bethey huey ( dekh raha hun?'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
4725,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi saye mein ho, phir wo (saya (us se buland ho jaey aur us shakhs ka kuch hissey dhoop mein ho jaey aur kuch saye main to wo (wahan sey) uth jaey.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
4726,"Hazrat Sharahus-sunnah mein Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne kaha : ''jab tum mein se koi saye mein ho aur wo saya us se buland ho jaey to wo shakhs ( wahan sey) uth jaey, kyonkey wo shetan ki majlis hai.'' Maamer ne isi tarah usey moquf riwayat kya hai. (rawahu fi Sharahus-sunnah ( ."
4727,"Hazrat abu-Usaid Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna jabkey aap masjid se bahar tashrif la rahey they, raastey mein mard aurton ke sath shamil ho gaey, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne aurton se farmaya : ''raastey ke eik taraf chalo, tumhen raastey ke beech mein chalney ka koi haq nahin, lihaza tum raastey ke kinaron par chalo .'' chunanche (ye hukm sun kar) aurat ( chaltey waqt ( deewar ke sath lag jati thi yahan tak ke uska kapda deewar ke sath atak jata tha. ( rawahu Abu-Dawood w al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( ."
4728,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mana farmaya ke aadmi do aurton ke darmiyan chaley. rawahu Abu-Dawood .
4729,"Hazrat Jabir bin Samra (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab ham Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hotey to ham mein se her shakhs ko jahan jagah milti wo wahin beth jata tha. rawahu Abu-Dawood . aur Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) do hadisein (baabul-qiyam) mein zikr ki gaee hain, aur Ali w Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) do hadisein ham inshaAllah Taala (baab Asmaunnabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) w صفاتہ ( mein zikr karengey ."
4730,"Hazrat Amr bin Shareed apney baap se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha : main is tarah betha hua tha ke maine apna baayan haath apni pusht ke peechey rakha hua tha aur daain haath ke angoothey ki jad ke paas jo gosht hai is par tek lagai thi, usi haalat mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) merey paas se guzrey to aapney farmaya : kya tum un logon ki tarah bethtey ho jin par ghazab hua (yani yahood).'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
4731,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) merey paas se guzrey jabkey main apney pet ke bal leta hua tha. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apney paaon se mujhey chaunka maara aur farmaya : ''Jundub! ye to jahannamiyon ka sa letna hai.'' rawahu ibne-Maja ."
4732,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' be-shak Allah chhinkney ko pasand farmata hai aur jamaai leney ko napasand farmata hai. jab tum mein se koi chheenk maarey aur) '' اَلْحَمْدُ لِلہِ '' ( kahey, to usey sunney waley her musalman par lazim hai ke wo usey ( '' یَرْحَمُکَ اللہُ '') Allah tum par rehem farmaai '' kahey. rahi jamaai to wo shetan ki taraf se hai, jab tum mein se koi jamaai leta hai to wo rokney ki maqdoor bhar koshish karey, kyonkey jab tum mein se koi jamaai leta hai to shetan us se muskraata hai.'' Bukhari . aur sahih Muslim ki riwayat mein hai : '' kyonkey tum mein se koi eik ( jamaai ke waqt ( aawaz nikalta hai to shetan us se hanstaa hai.'' Bukhari w Muslim ."
4733,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi chheenk maarey to wo (اَلْحَمْدُ لِلہِ ( kahey aur uska ( musalman ( bhai ya uska sathi usey ( یَرْحَمُکَ اللہُ ( kahiye, jab wo usey ( یَرْحَمُکَ اللہُ ( kahey to ye ( chheenk maarne wala) kahey: Allah tumhen hidayat dey aur tumhari haalat durust kar dey .'' Bukhari ."
4734,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, do aadmiyon ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas chheenk maari to aapney un mein se eik ko chheenk ka jawab diya jabkey doosrey ko na kaha, to us shakhs ne arz kya, Allah ke Rasool! aapney uskey liye dua farmaai jabkey merey liye dua nahin farmaai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''isliye ke usney ''alhamdulillah'' kaha, jabkey tum ne ''alhamdulillah'' nahin kaha.'' muttafaq aleh."
4735,"Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''jab tum mein se koi chheenk maarey aur ''alhamdulillah'' kahey to tum usey dua do. aur agar wo ''alhamdulillah'' na kahey to tum uskey liye dua na karo.'' rawahu Muslim ."
4736,"Hazrat Salma bin Akwa (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko suna, jabkey eik aadmi ne aap ke paas chheenk maari, to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uskey liye kaha : ( یَرْحَمُکَ اللہُ ( phir usney dusri martaba chheenk maari to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''bandey ko zukaam laga hua hai.'' aur Tirmizi ki riwayat mein hai ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey teesri martaba (chheenk aaney par) farmaya ke ''usey zukaam laga hua hai.'' rawahu Muslim w Tirmizi."
4737,Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se kisi ko jamaai aaye to wo apna haath apney munh par rakhey kyonkey shetan (munh mein) dakhil ho jata hai.'' rawahu Muslim .
4738,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab chheenk maartey to aap apney haath ya apney kapdey se apna chehra dhanp letey aur uskey sath wo apni aawaz past kartey they. Tirmizi, Abu-Dawud, aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. rawahu Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood ."
4739,Hazrat Abu-Ayub (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi chheenk maarey to wo kahey : her haal par Allah ka shukr hai. aur jo shakhs usey jawab dey to wo kahey : Allah tum par rehem farmaey. aur wo ( chheenk maarney wala ( kahey: Allah tumhen hidayat dey aur tumhari haalat durust kar dey.'' rawahu Tirmizi w Darmi .
4740,"Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, yahood, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas is ummid par chheenk maara kartey they ke aap unhen (yarhamakullah) kahen, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) kaha kartey they : ''Allah tumhen hidayat dey aur tumhari haalat durust kar dey.'' rawahu Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood."
4741,"Hazrat Hilal bin Yusaf bayan kartey hain, ham Salim bin Ubaid ke sath they ke itney mein logon mein se eik aadmi ne chheenk maari to usney kaha : Assalamualaikum ! (ye sun kar) Salim ne kaha : tujh par aur teri maa par, goya us aadmi ne apney dil mein kuchh narazi mehsus ki, unhoney farmaya : sun lo ! maine tumhen sirf wohi kuchh kaha hai jo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne kaha tha (eik dafa) eik aadmi ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas chheenk maari to usney kaha : Assalamualaikum ! Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tujh par aur teri maa par, (phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya) jab tum mein se koi chheenk maarey to wo (اَلْحَمْدُ لِلہِ رَبَّ الْعَالَمِیْنَ) kahe, aur jo usey jawab dey to wo kahey : ( یَرْحَمُکَ اللہُ ), aur phir wo kahey : Allah mujhey aur tumhen bakhsh dey.'' rawahu Tirmizi aur Abu-Dawood."
4742,"Hazrat Ubaid bin Rifaa (Raziallahu anhu), Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''chheenk maarney waley ko teen martaba dua'aiya jawab do, wo agar us se ziyada martaba chheenk maarey to phir agar tum chaho to usey dua'aiya jawab do aur agar tum chaho to (jawab) na do.'' Abu-Dawud, Tirmizi, aur unhoney farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Abu-Dawood aur Tirmizi."
4743,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain : ''apney (musalman) bhai ko (chheenk maarney ke jawab mein) teen baar dua'aiya jawab do, agar chheenkoon mein izafa ho jaey to wo zukaam hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood. aur unhon (raawi Saeed Maqbari) ne kaha : main unke mutalliq yehi janta hun ke unhoney hadees ko Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki taraf marfoo kiya hai."
4744,"Hazrat Naafe (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke eik aadmi ne ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ke pehlu mein chheenk maari to kaha : ''Allah ke liye tamam tareefen hain, aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) par salam ho, (ye sun kar) ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : main bhi kehta hun : her qism ki hamd Allah ke liye hai, aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) par salam ho. magar is tarah kehna Sabit nahin hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamein sikhaya tha ke ham kahin : her haal par Allah ka shukr hai. Tirmizi, aur unhoney farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
4745,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko khilkhila-kar hanstay huey nahin dekha ke main aap ke halaq ka kawwa dekh sakun , aap to sirf muskuraayaa kartey they. Bukhari."
4746,"Hazrat Jarir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine jab se Islam qubul kiya hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey (majlis mein aaney sey) mana nahin kiya aur aap jab bhi mujhey dekhtey to muskuraatey. muttafaq aleh."
4747,"Hazrat Jabir bin Samura (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jis jagah Namaz padhtey to wahan se tulu aaftaab tak nahin uthtey they, aur jab Suraj tulu ho jata to aap khadey hotey , aur (us doran ( Sahaba kiram (Raziallahu anhu) baaten kartey aur jahiliyat ke mamlaat par guftgu kiya kartey aur hanstay they jabkey aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) faqat tabassum farmaya kartey they. aur Tirmizi ki riwayat mein hai : wo she'r padha kartey they. rawahu Muslim aur Tirmizi."
4748,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Haris bin Juz (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se ziyada kisi ko muskuraatey huey nahin dekha. rawahu Tirmizi."
4749,"Hazrat Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha gaya : kya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke Sahaba hansa kartey they? unhoney farmaya : haan ! aur unke dilon mein eman pahad se bhi ziyada azeem tha. aur Bilal bin Saad (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, wo teer andazi kartey they aur eik doosrey ki taraf dekh kar hanstey they, aur jab raat ho jati to wo raahib (yani taarike-duniya) bin jatey they ( Allah ki ibadat mein masroof ho jatey they). (rawahu fi Sharahus-sunnah)."
4750,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) baazar mein they ke kisi aadmi ne kaha : Abul-Qaasim ! jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) uski taraf mutawajjeh huey to usney kaha : maine to usey bulaya tha, tab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''merey naam par naam rakho lekin meri kunniyat par kunniyat mat rakho.'' muttafaq aleh."
4751,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''merey naam par naam rakho aur meri kunniyat par kunniyat mat rakho , kyonkey mujhey to Qasim banaya gaya hai, main tumharey beech taqseem karta hun.'' muttafaq aleh."
4752,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tumharey namon mein se Abdullah aur Abdur-Rahman Allah ko ziyada pasand hain.'' rawahu Muslim."
4753,"Hazrat Samura bin Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''apney ghulam (bachchey ya ghulam) ka naam Yasar (aasani), Ribah (faayde), najeeh (kamiyab) aur Aflah (fauz aur falah) mat rakho , kyonkey tum kahogey : kya wo yahan hai? wo nahin hoga to kehney wala kahega : wo nahin hai.'' aur unhin ki riwayat mein hai, farmaya : ''apney ghulam ka Ribah , Yasar , Aflah aur Naafe naam na rakho.'' rawahu Muslim."
4754,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne irada farmaya ke wo Ya'alaa, Barka (barkat) , Aflah , Yasar , Naafe aur is tarah ke naam rakhney se mana farma den, phir maine aap ko dekha ke aapney baad mein is se khamoshi ikhtiyar farmaee, phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) wafat pa gaey aur is se mana na farmaya. rawahu Muslim."
4755,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : roze-qiyamat Allah ke yahan us shakhs ka naam sab se ziyada qabeeh hoga jis ka naam shahanshaah rakha gaya ho.'' Bukhari. aur Muslim ki riwayat mein hai farmaya : ''roze-qiyamat Allah ke yahan wo shakhs sab se ziyada naraz kun aur khabees naam wala hoga jis ka naam shahanshaah rakha gaya hoga halanke shahanshaah to sirf Allah hi hai. muttafaq aleh."
4756,"Hazrat Zenab binte-Abi Salma (Raziallahu anhu) bayan karti hain, mera naam Barra rakha gaya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum apni tareef khud na kiya karo, tum mein se jo nek hain, Allah unhen khub janta hai iska naam Zenab rakho.'' rawahu Muslim."
4757,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Juweriya (Raziallahu anhu) ka naam Barra tha, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unka naam badal kar Juweriya rakh diya, aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) napasand kartey they ke yun kaha jaey : wo Barra ke paas se chaley gaey hain. rawahu Muslim."
4758,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke umr (Raziallahu anhu) ki eik beti ko Aasiya kaha jata tha, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uska naam Jameela rakh diya. rawahu Muslim."
4759,"Hazrat Sehal bin Saad (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Munzir bin Abi Usaid jab paida huey to usey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein laya gaya, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey apni raan par rakha aur farmaya : ''iska naam kya hai?'' usney kaha : falan, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''nahin, balke uska naam Munzir hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
4760,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum mein se koi yun na kahe : merey bandey (ghulam) meri bandi (londi), tum sab Allah ke bandey aur ghulam ho jabkey tumhari sab khawatin Allah ki londiyan hain, balke tum yun kaha karo : merey ladkey , meri ladki , aur ghulam bhi yun na kahe : merey rab ! balke yun kahey : merey aaqa.'' eik dusri riwayat mein hai : wo yun kahe : merey sayed, merey maula.'' eik dusri riwayat mein hai : ''ghulam apney aaqa se merey maula na kahe, kyonkey tumhara maula Allah hai.'' rawahu Muslim."
4761,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum (angoor ko) karam na kaho , kyonkey karam to momin ka dil hai.'' rawahu Muslim."
4762,"Aur Muslim hi ki Waael bin Hajar (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hadees mein hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum karam na kaho , balke tum inab aur habla (angoor) kaho.'' rawahu Muslim."
4763,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum angoor ka naam karam rakho na zamaney ko bura kaho , kyonkey Allah hi to zamana hai.'' Bukhari."
4764,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum mein se koi zamaney ko bura bhala na kahe, kyonkey Allah hi to zamana hai.'' rawahu Muslim."
4765,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum mein se koi shakhs ye na kahe : mera nafs (ji) khabees ho gaya balke yun kahe : mera nafs bojhal ho gaya.'' muttafaq aleh. aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hadees : ''ibne-Adam mujhey eza (takleef) pahunchata hai.'' (باب الایمان) mein zikr ho chuki hai."
4766,"Hazrat Shureh bin Haani apney walid se riwayat kartey hain ke jab wo apni qom ke sath Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aaye to aapney unhen suna ke wo merey walid ko Abul-Hakam ki kunniyat se pukartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen bula kar farmaya : ''be-shak Allah hi hukm hai aur hukm ka ikhtiyar usey hi hasil hai, tumhari kunniyat Abul-Hakam kyon rakhi gaee?'' usney kaha : jab meri qom mein kisi chiz mein ikhtilaf ho jata to wo merey paas aatey aur main unke darmiyan faisla kar deta hun to wo dono fariq merey faisley par razi ho jatey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye kitna achchha hai, terey kitney bachchey hain?'' usney kaha : Shureh, Muslim aur Abdullah. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''in mein se bada kon hai? '' raawi bayan kartey hain, maine kaha : Shureh, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum Abu Shureh ho.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood aur Nasai."
4767,"Hazrat Masruq bayan kartey hain, main umr (Raziallahu anhu) se mila to unhoney farmaya : tum kon ho? maine kaha : Masruq bin Ajdaa, umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : '' Ajdaa, shetan (ka naam) hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood aur ibne-Maja."
4768,"Hazrat Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''roze-qiyamat tumhen tumharey aur tumharey baap-daada ke naam se pukara jaeyga, apney naam achchey rakho.'' rawahu Ahmed aur Abu-Dawood."
4769,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne us se mana farmaya ke koi shakhs apney naam aur apni kunniyat ko is tarah ikhatta karkey Muhammad Abul-Qaasim naam rakh ley. rawahu Tirmizi.
4770,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum merey naam par naam rakho to phir meri kunniyat par kunniyat mat rakho.'' aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai, aur Abu-Dawood ki riwayat mein hai, farmaya : ''jisney merey naam par naam rakha to wo meri kunniyat na rakhey, aur jisney meri kunniyat par kunniyat rakhi to wo merey naam par naam na rakhey.'' rawahu Tirmizi, ibne-Maja aur Abu-Dawood."
4771,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke eik aurat ne arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! merey yahan eik bachcha paida hua hai aur maine uska naam Muhammad aur uski kunniyat Abul-Qaasim rakhi hai, lekin mujhey pata chala hai ke aap isey napasand farmatey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kon hai wo jisney halal qarar diya mera naam rakhna aur haram kiya meri kunniyat rakhna, ya kon hai wo jisney haram kiya meri kunniyat rakhna aur halal kiya mera naam rakhna?'' Abu-Dawud, aur Muhiussunnah (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Abu-Dawood."
4772,"Hazrat Muhammad bin Hanfiya apney walid se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha : maine arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! mujhey bataeyn agar aap ke baad merey yahan bachcha paida ho to main aap ke naam par uska naam aur aap ki kunniyat par uski kunniyat rakh lun? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''haan.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
4773,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main eik buti chuna karta tha, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne is par meri kunniyat (Abu-Hamza) rakhi. isey Tirmizi ne bayan kiya aur farmaya : is hadees ko ham sirf isi tareeqe se jantey hain, aur masaabeh mein hai ke usney usey sahih qarar diya hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
4774,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) bura naam tabdeel kar diya kartey they. rawahu Tirmizi.
4775,"Hazrat Bashir bin Memun apney chacha Usama bin Akhdari se riwayat kartey hain ke Isram naami eik aadmi un logon mein shamil tha jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aaye they, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tumhara naam kya hai?'' usney kaha : Isram, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''nahin, balke tum Zar'a ho.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
4776,"Aur Abu-Dawood ne kaha, aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Aas, Aziz ,Atla, Shetan , Hukm , Ghurab , Hubaab aur Shahab naam badal diye they, aur unhoney kaha : maine ikhtisaar ki khatir unki sanad bayan nahin kin. rawahu Abu-Dawood."
4777,"Hazrat Abu-Masood Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhoney Abu Abdullah se ya Abu Abdullah ne Abu Masood se kaha : tum ne lafz (زَعَمُوْا) (logon ka khayal hai) ke barey mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko kya farmatey huey suna? unhoney kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''aadmi ka aisey andaz mein guftgu karna bura hai.'' Abu-Dawud, aur unhoney kaha : Abu Abdullah se murad Huzefa hain. rawahu Abu-Dawood."
4778,"Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''yun na kaha karo : jo Allah chahey aur falan chahey, balke yun kaho : jo Allah chahey, phir falan chahey.'' rawahu Ahmed aur Abu-Dawood."
4779,"Aur eik munqata' riwayat mein hai, farmaya : ''yun na kaha karo : jo Allah chahey aur jo Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) chahey , balke yun kaha karo : jo akela Allah chahey.'' (rawahu fi Sharahus-sunnah)."
4780,"Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''munafiq ke liye lafz sayed (aaqa) na kaho, kyonkey agar wo sayed (sardar, aaqa) hai to tum ne apney rab ko naraz kar diya.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
4781,"Hazrat Abdul Humed bin Juber bin Sheba bayan kartey hain, main Saeed bin Musaiyeb ke paas betha tha, unhoney mujhey hadees bayan ki ke unke dada Huzn , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aaye to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne daryaft farmaya : ''tumhara naam kya hai?'' usney kaha : mera naam Huzn hai. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''(nahin) balke tum Sehal ho.'' usney kaha : main apney walid ke rakhey huey naam ko tabdeel nahin karunga, ibne Musaiyeb ne farmaya : iskey baad ham mein ''حزونت'' (sakhti) barqarar rahi. Bukhari."
4782,"Hazrat Abu-Wahab Jushmi bayan kartey hain, unhoney kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''anbiya (Alaihissalam) ke namon par naam rakha karo, Allah ke yahan pasandida naam Abdullah aur Abdur Rehman hain, sab se sachcha naam Haris aur Hammam hai jabkey sab se qabeeh naam Harab aur Murra hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
4783,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, do aadmi mashriq ki (janib) se aaye aur unhoney khitab kiya, logon ne unke bayan par tajjub kiya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''be-shak baaz bayan jadu ki si taaseer rakhtey hain.'' Bukhari."
4784,"Hazrat Ubai bin Kab (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''be-shak baaz she'r pur-hikmat hotey hain.'' Bukhari."
4785,"Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''takalluf se kalam karney waley halak ho gaey.'' aapney teen martaba yehi farmaya. rawahu Muslim."
4786,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''sab se ziyada durust baat jo kisi shayer ne kahi wo Labid shayer ki ye baat hai : sun lo ! Allah ke siwa her chiz faani hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
4787,"Hazrat Amr bin Shareed apney walid se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha : main eik roz Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke peechhey sawar tha aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya tumhen Umayya bin Abi Salat ka koi she'r yad hai?'' maine arz kiya : ji haan ! aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''sunaao !'' maine aap ko eik she'r sunaya , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aur sunaao !'' phir maine aap ko eik aur she'r sunaya, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aur sunaao !'' yahan tak ke maine aap ko so she'r sunaye. rawahu Muslim."
4788,Hazrat Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) kisi ghazwe mein shareek they ke aap ki ungli se khoon nikalney laga to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''eik ungli hi to ho jo khoon aalooda hui hai aur tujhey jo takleef pahunchi hai wo Allah ki raah mein hai.'' muttafaq aleh.
4789,"Hazrat Bara (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne banu Qureza (ke muhaasrey) ke din Hassan bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya : ''mushrikon ki tauheen bayan karo, Allah (ki nusrat) tumharey sath hai.'' aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Hassan (Raziallahu anhu) se farma rahey they : ''meri taraf se jawab do , aey Allah ! Jibrael (Alaihissalam) ke zariey uski madad farma.'' muttafaq aleh."
4790,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke unhoney kaha, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''Quraish ki tauheen bayan karo kyonkey ye un par teer andazi se bhi ziyada shadeed hai.'' rawahu Muslim."
4791,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko Hassan (Raziallahu anhu) se farmatey huey suna : ''jab tak tum Allah aur uskey Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke difaa mein mushrekin ki hijo (tauheen) kartey rehtey ho us waqt tak Jibrael (Alaihissalam) tumhari madad kartey rehtey hain.'' Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''Hassaan ne unki hijo (tauheen) bayan ki aur musalmanon ko sukoon pahunchaya aur khud bhi sukoon paya.'' rawahu Muslim."
4792,"Hazrat Bara (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) khandaq ke roz mitti utha rahey they yahan tak ke unka pet ghubar aalud ho gaya, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) (asha'aar) keh rahey they : ''Allah ki qism ! agar Allah hamein hidayat na deta to ham hidayat yafta na hotey , sadqa detey aur na hi Namaz padhtey , ham par sakeenat nazil farmana jab ham un (deen ke dushman) se milen to hamein Sabit qom rakh kyonkey unhoney ham par ziyadti ki hai, jab bhi unhoney fitney ka irada kiya to ham ne inkar kiya.'' aap lafz ''ham ne inkar kiya, ham ne inkar kiya, par aawaz buland farmatey they.'' muttafaq aleh."
4793,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Muhajir aur Ansaar (Sahaba kiram (Raziallahu anhu)) khandaq khod rahey they, mitti utha rahey they aur keh rahey they : ham wo log hain jinhon ne taa-hayaat jihad karney par Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki baiat ki hai. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) unke jawab mein farma rahey they : ''aey Allah ! zindagi to aakhirat ki zindagi hai, ansaar aur muhajrin ki maghfirat farma.'' muttafaq aleh."
4794,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kisi aadmi ke pet ka peep se bhar kar kharab ho jana , us se behtar hai ke uska pet (mazmoom) ashaar se bhar jaey.'' muttafaq aleh."
4795,Hazrat Kab bin Maalik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se arz kiya ke Allah Taala ne she'r ki mazammat ke barey mein hukm utara hai. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''be-shak momin apni talwaar aur apni zaban se jihad karta hai. us zaat ki qism jiskey haath mein meri jaan hai ! (ye hijo (tauheen) is tarah hai) goya tum un par teer andazi kar rahey ho.''استیعاب لابن عبدالبر mein hai ke unhoney arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! aap she'r ke mutalliq kya farmatey hain? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' be-shak momin apni talwaar aur apni zaban ke sath jihad karta hai.'' (rawahu fi Sharahus-sunnah).
4796,"Hazrat Abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' haya aur kam-goi eman ki shaakhen hain, jabkey fohsh-goi aur bayan (mubaalgha aaraai) nifaq ki do shaakhen hain.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
4797,"Hazrat Abu-Solba Khushni (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' be-shak (duniya mein) tum mein se mujhey ziyada pasand aur mehbub aur roze-qiyamat merey ziyada qarib wo shakhs hoga jo tum mein se ziyada baa-akhlaaq hoga, aur tum mein se (duniya mein) mujhey sab se ziyada napasand aur roze-qiyamat mujh se sab se ziyada door wo shakhs hoga jo tum mein se bad-akhlaq, bahut baaten karney waley, zaban daraz aur gala phaad kar baaten karney waley hain.'' (rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan)."
4798,"Hazrat Imam Tirmizi ne Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se isi tarah riwayat kiya hai, unki riwayat mein hai, Sahaba kiram (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! ham baatuni aur munh phat shakhs ke mutalliq to jantey hain, lekin ''المتفیھقون'' se murad kon hain? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''takabbur karney waley.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
4799,"Hazrat Saad bin Abi Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''qiyamat qaaim nahin hogi yahan tak ke eik qom ka zuhoor hoga wo apni zabanon ke zariey (midha saraai karkey maal kama kar) aisey khaeyn-gey jaisey gaaey apni zaban ke sath khati hai.'' rawahu Ahmed."
4800,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''be-shak Allah charb-zaban aur mubaalghe se kaam leney waley us shakhs se dushmani rakhta hai jo zaban ki kamai khata hai jaise ke gaaey zaban se chaara khati hai.'' Tirmizi, Abu-Dawud, aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi aur Abu-Dawood."
4801,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Mairaj ki raat mein kuch aisey logon ke paas se guzra jinkey hont aag ki qenchiyon se kaatey ja rahey they, maine kaha : Jibrael! ye kon log hain? unhoney kaha : ye aap ki ummat ke khateeb hazraat hain, jinkey qol w fel (kathni aur karni) mein tazaad tha.'' Tirmizi, aur unhoney farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
4802,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs kalam sirf isliye seekhta hai taake wo uskey zariey mardon ya logon ke dilon par qabu pa sakey to roze-qiyamat Allah uski taraf se koi nafl aur farz ibadat qubul nahin kerega.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
4803,"Hazrat Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhoney eik roz farmaya eik aadmi khada hua to usney (izhar fasaahat ke liye) baat ko tool diya to Amr (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : agar ye baat kartey waqt miyaanaa rawi ikhtiyar karta to uskey liye behtar hota, kyonkey maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''maine jana ya mujhey hukm diya gaya ke main baat mein ikhtisaar karun, kyonkey ikhtisaar behtar hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
4804,"Hazrat Sakhr bin Abdullah bin Barida apney walid se aur wo apney dada se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''be-shak baaz bayan jadu jaisa asar rakhtey hain, baaz ilm jihalat hotey hain, baaz sher hikmat hotey hain aur baaz qol bojh hotey hain.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
4805,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam), Hassan (Raziallahu anhu) ke liye masjid mein member rakhwaatey, wo is par khadey ho kar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki taraf se fakhr kartey ya aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka difaa kartey, aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farmatey : '' be-shak Allah Jibrael (Alaihissalam) ke zariey Hassan ki madad farmata hai jab tak wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki taraf se difaa karta hai ya fakhr karta hai.'' Bukhari"
4806,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, eik shakhs aap ka hudi khuwan tha usey Anjasha ke naam se yad kya jata tha, uski aawaz bahut achi thi, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey farmaya : ''Anjasha! thehro-thehro, shishon ko mat choor karo.'' Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : aapney ye khawatin ki nazakat ke peshe-nazar farmaya tha. muttafaq aleh."
4807,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas sher zikr kya gaya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''wo eik kalam hai, is mein se jo achcha hai wo achcha hai aur jo bura hai wo bura hai.'' rawahu Dar-Qutni ."
4808,Hazrat Imam Shafai (Raziallahu anhu) ne usey Urwa se mursal riwayat kya hai. rawahu Shafai .
4809,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath ( Yamen ke ilaqey ( araj mein safar kar rahey they ke eik shayer samney aaya aur wo ashaar kehney laga, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''(us) shetan ko pakdo.'' ya farmaya : '' (us) shetan ko (sher kehney sey) roko, ye ke kisi aadmi ke pet ka peep se bharna uskey liye sher ke sath bharney se behtar hai.'' rawahu Muslim ."
4810,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' gaana dil mein nifaq paida kar deta hai jis tarah pani kheti uga deta hai.'' ( rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( ."
4811,"Hazrat Naafe bayan kartey hain, main ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath eik raastey mein tha to unhoney baansurii ki aawaz suni , to unhoney apni dono ungliyan apney dono kanon mein dal lein , aur wo raastey mein dusri janib hat gaey, phir door ja kar mujhey farmaya : Naafe ! kya tum kuch sun rahey ho? maine kaha : nahin, unhoney kanon se ungliyan nikalin aur farmaya : main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath tha aapney baansuri ki aawaz suni, to aapney aisey hi kya tha jaisey maine kya, Naafe ne kaha : main tab chhota tha. rawahu Ahmed w Abu-Dawood ."
4812,"Hazrat Sehal bin Saad (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs mujhey zaban aur sharm-gah ( ki hifazat ( ki zamanat dey dey to main usey jannat ki zamanat deta hun.'' Bukhari ."
4813,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' be-shak banda aisi baat karta hai jis mein Allah ki raza hoti hai aur wo usey koi ahmiyat nahin deta, lekin Allah uski wajeh se darjaat buland farma deta hai, aur banda aisi baat karta hai jis mein Allah ki narazi hoti hai aur wo usey koi ahmiyat nahin deta , lekin wo uskey baais jahannam mein gir jata hai.'' ye alfaz Bukhari ke hain. aur Bukhari , Muslim ki riwayat mein hai : '' wo us ( baat ( ki wajeh se jahannam mein is qadr gehra gir jata hai jis qadr mashriq w maghrib ke darmiyan doorii hai.'' Bukhari w Muslim ."
4814,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' musalman ko gaali dena fisq aur us se ladaai jhagda karna kufr hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
4815,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ne apney ( musalman ( bhai se kaha : kafir, to un dono mein se eik zarur ( eman sey) kufr ki taraf lota .'' muttafaq aleh."
4816,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar koi shakhs kisi shakhs ko fasiq ya kafir keh kar pukarta hai aur agar wo shakhs ( jisey pukara ja raha hai) aisey na ho to phir wo ( baat (us ( kehney waley ( par lot aati hai.'' Bukhari ."
4817,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ne kisi shakhs ko kafir keh kar pukara ya kaha : Allah ke dushman! jabkey wo aisey na ho to wo baat us (kehney waley ( par lot aati hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
4818,Hazrat Anas aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aapas mein gaali galoch karney waley do afrad mein se us waqt tak gunehgar wo hai jo pehley gaali deta hai jab tak mazloom eik ke badley mein do gaaliyaan na dey.'' rawahu Muslim .
4819,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' sachey shakhs ke liye munasib nahin ke wo bahut ziyada lanat karney wala ho.'' rawahu Muslim .
4820,"Hazrat abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''kasrat se lanat karney waley roze-qiyamat na gawah hongey aur na sifarishi.'' rawahu Muslim ."
4821,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab aadmi kehta hai : log (apney burey aamaal ke badley mein) halak ho gaey to wo un sab se ziyada halak honey wala hai.'' rawahu Muslim ."
4822,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum qiyamat ke roz sab se bad-tareen us shakhs ko paaogey jo doghla hai, udhar logon se kuch baat karta hai aur udhar logon se kuch baat karta hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
4823,"Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''chughal khor jannat mein nahin jaeyga.'' aur Muslim ki riwayat mein) نَمَّامٌ ( '' chughal khor '' ka lafz hai. muttafaq aleh."
4824,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' sachai ko ikhtiyar karo, kyonkey sachai neki ki taraf raahnumai karti hai, aur neki jannat ki taraf raahnumai karti hai, aadmi sach boltaa rehta hai aur sachai ka mutalaashi rehta hai yahan tak ke wo Allah ke yahan Siddiq ( bahut sacha ( likh diya jata hai, aur tum jhoot se bacho , kyonkey jhoot gunahon ki taraf raahnumai karta hai aur gunah jahannam ki taraf raahnumai kartey hain, aadmi jhoot boltaa rehta hai aur jhoot ka talabgar rehta hai yahan tak ke wo Allah ke yahan jhoota likh diya jata hai.'' aur Muslim ki riwayat mein hai, farmaya : '' be-shak sach neki hai, aur neki jannat ki taraf raahnumai karti hai, aur be-shak jhoot gunah hai, aur gunah jahannam ki taraf raahnumai kartey hain.'' muttafaq aleh."
4825,"Hazrat Umme- kulsoom (Raziallahu anhu) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' logon ke darmiyan suleh karaney wala shakhs jhoota nahin, wo khair w bhalai ki baat karta hai aur khair w bhalai ki baat hi aagey pahunchata hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
4826,"Hazrat Miqdad bin Aswad (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum madah saraai karney walon ko dekho to unke chehron par mitti phenko.'' rawahu Muslim ."
4827,"Hazrat abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, eik aadmi ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki mojudgi mein doosrey aadmi ki tareef ki to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''teri tabahi ho, tum ne apney bhai ki gardan kaat di.'' aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ye teen martaba farmaya'' jisney zarur hi madah saraai kerni ho to wo kahey : main falan ko is is tarah khayal karta hun, jabkey Allah uski haqiqat se aagah hai, agar mausoof aisa hi ho jaisa usney khayal kya, wo Allah par kisi shakhs ki nisbat tazkiye ka hukm yaqeeni taur par na lagaey.'' muttafaq aleh."
4828,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya tum jantey ho gheebat kya hai? '' Sahaba kiram (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya, Allah aur uskey Rasool behtar jantey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' tera apney bhai ko in alfaz se yad karna jisey , wo napasand karta ho.'' arz kya gaya, aap mujhey bataeyn ke jo baat mein kar raha hun wo merey bhai main mojud ho to phir? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar to wo chiz is mein hai jo tum keh rahey ho to phir tum ne uski gheebat ki, aur jab tum ne aisi baat ki jo is mein nahin to phir tum ne is par bohtan lagaya.'' eik dusri riwayat mein hai : ''jab tum ne apney bhai ke mutalliq aisi baat ki jo is mein hai to tum ne uski gheebat ki, aur jab tum ne aisi baat ki jo is mein nahin hai to phir tum ne is par bohtan bazi ki.'' rawahu Muslim ."
4829,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke eik aadmi ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se andar aaney ki ijazat talab ki to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''usey ijazat de-do aur wo apni qom ka bura shakhs hai.'' jab wo beth gaya to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apney chehrey par khushi ka izhar farmaya aur uskey liye tabassum farmaya : jab wo aadmi chala gaya to Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! aapney uskey mutalliq is tarah is tarah kaha, phir (uskey aaney par) aapney apney chehrey par khushi ka izhar farmaya aur uskey liye tabassum farmaya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum ne mujhey Kab fohsh bhale hi paya? kyonkey roze-qiyamat Allah ke yahan maqam w martaba mein sab se badtar wo shakhs hoga jiskey shar se bachney ke liye log usey chhod den.'' eik dusri riwayat mein hai : ''uski fohsh goi se bachney ke liye .'' muttafaq aleh."
4830,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''meri sari ummat ke gunah qabile-maafi hain, magar wo log jo elaaniya gunah kartey hain, aur elaaniya gunah karna ye hai ke aadmi raat ke waqt koi (gunah ka ( amal karey, phir subh honey par kehta phirey : aey falan! maine raat ko is tarah is tarah kya tha, halanke Allah ne uski parda poshi ki hui thi, aur usney raat is tarah basar ki ke uskey rab ne usey chupa rakha tha aur jab subh karta hai to apney ooper se Allah ke pardey ko utha deta hai.'' muttafaq aleh. aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hadees : ''jo shakhs Allah par eman rakhta ho.'' ( baabul-ziyafa) mein zikr ki gaee hai."
4831,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs jhoot bolnaa chhod deta hai dar-aan-haaleke wo batil par tha. uskey liye jannat ke kinarey par eik ghar bana diya jata hai, aur jisney haq par hotey huey bhi jhagda tarak kar diya to uskey liye jannat ke wast mein ghar bana diya jata hai, aur jisney apna akhlaq sanwaar liya , uskey liye is mein buland jagah par ghar bana diya jata hai.'' Imam Tirmizi ne is hadees ko bayan kya hai aur usey Hasan kaha hai, aur isi tarah Sharahus-sunnah aur masaabeh mein hai, farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. ( rawahu Tirmizi w fi Sharahus-sunnah ( ."
4832,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya tum jantey ho ke kon si chiz ziyada tar logon ko jannat mein dakhil karegi ? ( phir farmaya ( Allah ka taqwa aur Hasan khalq , kya tum jantey ho ke kon si chiz ziyada tar logon ko jahannam mein dakhil karegi ? ( phir farmaya ( do chizen , munh aur sharm-gah .'' rawahu Tirmizi w ibne-Maja ."
4833,"Hazrat Bilal bin Haris (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''be-shak aadmi bhalai ki baat karta hai aur wo uski qadr w manzilat se aagah nahin hota jiskey badla mein Allah us shakhs ke liye roze-qiyamat tak apni raza likh deta hai, aur be-shak aadmi koi buri baat kar deta hai aur wo uski bhi ahmiyat nahin janta to uski wajeh se Allah roze-qiyamat tak ke liye apni narazi likh deta hai.'' Sharahus-sunnah . aur Imam malik, Tirmizi aur ibne-Maja ne usi ki misl riwayat kya hai. (rawahu fi Sharahus-sunnah w Malik w Tirmizi w ibne-Maja ( ."
4834,"Hazrat Behaz bin Hakim apney walid se aur wo apney dada se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' us shakhs ke liye halakat hai jo baat kartey waqt jhoot bolta hai taake wo uskey zariey logon ko hansaaey, to uskey liye halakat hai, uskey liye halakat hai.'' rawahu Ahmed w Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood w Darmi ."
4835,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''be-shak banda mehaz logon ko hansaaney ke liye baat karta hai aur wo uski wajeh se zamin w aasman ki darmiyani masafat se bhi ziyada door jahannam mein gir jata hai, aur wo apney paaon ki taraf se phisalney se itna nahin phisalta jitna ke wo zaban ke phisalney se phisaltaa hai.'' (rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan) ."
4836,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jisney khamoshi ikhtiyar ki usney najat pai .'' (rawahu Ahmed w Tirmizi w Darmi w al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan) ."
4837,"Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se mulaqat ki aur maine arz kya, najat ka baais kya chiz hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''apni zaban par qabu rakh, tera ghar terey liye kafi hona chahiye, aur apni khataaon par roya kar .'' rawahu Ahmed w Tirmizi ."
4838,"Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) ne is hadees ko marfoo riwayat kya hai, farmaya : ''jab ibne-Adam subh karta hai to sarey aaza zaban se darkhast kartey hain ke hamarey ( huquq ke tahaffuz ke) barey mein Allah se darna, kyonkey ham terey rehem w karam par hain, agar to sidhi rahi to ham bhi sidhey rahengey aur agar to tedhi ho gaee to ham bhi tedhey ho jaeyngey .'' rawahu Tirmizi ."
4839,"Hazrat Ali bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' aadmi ke Islam ki khoobi ye hai ke wo ghair mutalliqa ( fuzul baaton ( ko chhod dey .'' rawahu Malik w Ahmed ."
4840,Hazrat Imam ibne-Maja ne usey Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kya hai. rawahu ibne-Maja .
4841,Hazrat Imam Tirmizi aur Behaqi ne Shobil-emaan mein usey un dono ( Ali bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu) aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat kya hai. ( rawahu Tirmizi w al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( .
4842,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) mein se eik aadmi faut ho gaya to eik aadmi ne kaha : jannat ki basharat ho, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya tum nahin jantey ke shayad usney kisi ghair mutalliqa chiz ke barey mein baat ki ho ya kisi aisi chiz mein bukhl kya ho jo is mein kami nahin kar sakti thi.'' rawahu Tirmizi ."
4843,"Hazrat Sufiyan bin Abdullah Saqafi (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine arz kya : Allah ke Rasool! aap ko merey barey mein sab se ziyada kis chiz ka andesha hai? raawi bayan kartey hain : aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apni zaban pakad kar farmaya : ''iska.'' Tirmizi, aur unhoney usey sahih qarar diya hai. rawahu Tirmizi ."
4844,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab banda jhoot bolta hai to uski badboo ki wajeh se farishta us (bandey) se eik meel door chala jata hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi ."
4845,"Hazrat Sufiyan bin Asad Hizrami (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : '' badi khayanat ye hai ke to apney ( musalman ( bhai se koi baat karey, wo us main tumhen sacha janta ho jabkey to us se jhoot bol raha ho.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
4846,"Hazrat Ammar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs duniya mein doghla hoga to roze-qiyamat uski zaban aag ki hogi.'' rawahu Darmi ."
4847,"Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''momin na to taan karney wala hota hai aur na lanat karney wala, na wo fohsh bhale hi hota hai aur na zaban daraz .'' Tirmizi, Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan. aur Behaqi ki dusri riwayat mein hai, na wo fohsh goi karney wala hota hai aur na zaban darazi karney wala .'' Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. ( rawahu Tirmizi w al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( ."
4848,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' momin lanat karney wala nahin hota .'' eik dusri riwayat mein hai : '' momin ke liye munasib nahin ke wo lanat karney wala ho.'' rawahu Tirmizi ."
4849,"Hazrat Samra bin Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''eik doosrey ko aisey na kaho : tum par Allah ki lanat ho, tum par Allah ka ghazab ho aur tum jahannam mein jaao.'' aur eik riwayat mein hai : '' aisey bhi na kaho : tum (jahannam ki) aag mein jaao .'' rawahu Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood ."
4850,"Hazrat abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''jab banda kisi chiz par lanat bhejta hai to wo lanat aasman ki taraf chadhti hai, to uskey pahunchney se pehley aasman ke darwazey band kar diye jatey hain, phir wo zamin ki taraf utarti hai, uskey darwazey bhi band kar diye jatey hain, phir wo daeyn-baeyn jati hai, jab wo koi raasta nahin paati to wo us shakhs ki taraf jati hai jis par lanat ki gaee thi, b-sharte-ke wo uska mustahiq ho warna wo kehney waley ki taraf lot aati hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
4851,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke hua ne eik aadmi ki chadar uda di to usney is par lanat ki to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''us par lanat na bhejo kyonkey wo to hukm ki paband hai, aur jo shakhs kisi chiz par lanat bhejta hai, jabkey wo uski mustahiq nahin hoti to phir wo lanat usi shakhs par lot aati hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood ."
4852,"Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''mera koi sahabi kisi doosrey sahabi ke barey mein mujhey koi (na-pasandida) baat na pahunchaey, kyonkey main pasand karta hun ke jab main tumharey paas aaun to mera Sina saaf ho.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
4853,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se arz kya : aap ko Safiya (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se bas ye ye kafi hai yani unka qad chhota hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum ne eik aisi baat ki hai agar usey samandar mein mila diya jaey to is par ghalib aa jaey (yani uski keyfiyat badal daley) .'' rawahu Ahmed w Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood ."
4854,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''fohsh goi jis chiz mein ho, wo usey aibdar bana deti hai aur haya jis chiz mein ho wo usey muzayyan kar deta hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi ."
4855,"Hazrat Khalid bin Maadaan, Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs apney ( musalman ( bhai ko) uskey sabiqa kisi ( gunah par malamat karta hai to ye shakhs marney se pehley wo ( gunah ( kar leta hai.'' us se wo gunah murad hai jis se wo tauba kar chuka ho. Tirmizi, aur unhoney farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai, iski sanad muttasil nahin kyonkey Khalid ki Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) se mulaqat nahin hui. rawahu Tirmizi ."
4856,"Hazrat Waasila (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' apney ( musalman ( bhai (ke musibat mein mubtala honey) par khushi ka izhar na kar, mumkin hai Allah is par rehem farma dey aur tumhen (us musibat mein) mubtala kar dey .'' Tirmizi, aur unhoney farmaya : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi ."
4857,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main kisi ki naqal utaarna pasand nahin karta cahey mujhey itna itna maal diya jaey.'' Tirmizi ne usey riwayat kya aur usey sahih qarar diya hai. rawahu Tirmizi ."
4858,"Hazrat Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, eik eraab aaya, usney apna oont bithaya phir usey baandha aur masjid mein aaya, usney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke peechey Namaz padhi, jab aapney salam phera to wo apni sawari ke paas aaya, usey khola aur is par Sawar ho kar buland aawaz se kaha : aey Allah! mujh par aur Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) par rehem farma aur hamari rehmat mein kisi aur ko shareek na karna. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya tum guman kartey ho wo ziyada nadan hai ya uska oont? kya tum ne uski baat nahin suni?'' Sahaba kiram (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya, kyon nahin, suni hai. rawahu Abu-Dawood . aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hadees : '' bandey ke jhoota honey ke liye kafi hai.'' ( baab al-etisam) ki fasal awwal mein bayan ho chuki hai."
4859,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab fasiq ki taareef ki jati hai to rab taala naraz hota hai aur uski ( tareef ki) wajeh se uska arsh laraz jata hai.'' , ( rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( ."
4860,"Hazrat abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''momin mein khayanat aur jhoot ki aadat nahin ho sakti albatta inke alawa sab kuch ho sakta hai.'' rawahu Ahmed ."
4861,Hazrat Imam Behaqi ne Saad bin abi Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) se Shobil-emaan mein riwayat kya hai. ( rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( .
4862,"Hazrat Safwan bin سُلیم (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se arz kya gaya, kya momin buzdil ho sakta hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' haan .'' phir arz kya gaya : kya momin bakheel ho sakta hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' haan .'' phir aap se arz kya gaya, kya momin jhoota ho sakta hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' nahin .'' Malik , Behaqi ne usey Shobil-emaan mein mursal riwayat kya hai. ( rawahu Malik w al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( ."
4863,"Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, shetan insani roop dhaar kar logon ke paas aata hai, un se jhooti baaten karta hai, phir jab log muntashir ho jatey hain to un mein se eik aadmi kehta hai : maine eik aadmi ko suna . main uskey chehrey se shanaasa hun lekin main uska naam nahin janta, wo ye baat bayan karta tha.'' rawahu Muslim."
4864,"Hazrat Imran bin hitaan (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaya to maine unhen kaali chadar se got maarey huey masjid mein akeley paya to maine kaha : abu-Zar! ye tanhai kaisi? unhoney kaha, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''burey ham nasheen se tanhai behtar hai aur nek ham nasheen tanhai se behtar hai aur achi baat tehreer karna khamoshi se behtar hai jabkey buri baat tehreer karney se khamoshi behtar hai.'' ( rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( ."
4865,Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' aadmi ka ( buri baat karney sey) khamoshi barqarar rakhna saath baras ki ibadat se behtar hai.'' ( rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( .
4866,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua , unhoney puri hadees zikr ki aur yahan tak bayan kya, unhoney kaha, maine arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! mujhey wasiyat farmaeyn, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main tumhen Allah ka taqwa ikhtiyar karney ki wasiyat karta hun, kyonkey wo terey tamam maamlon ke liye ziyada baais zeenat hai.'' maine arz kya : mazeed farmaain ! aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Quran ki tilawat aur Allah azz-w-jall ka zikr kar kyonkey wo aasman mein terey tazakirey aur zamin mein terey liye Noor ka baais hai.'' maine arz kya : mujhey mazeed wasiyat farmaeyn, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' hamesha khamoshi ikhtiyar karo, kyonkey wo shetan ko door karney aur terey Deen ke mamley mein teri madadgar hai.'' maine arz kya, mazeed farmaeyn, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' ziyada hansney se bacho , kyonkey wo dil ko murda kar deta hai aur chehrey ke Noor ko khatam kar deta hai.'' maine arz kya : mazeed wasiyat farmaeyn, raawi bayan kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' haq bayan kar chahey wo kadwa ho.'' maine arz kya, mazeed farmaeyn, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ke mamley mein kisi malamat gar ki malamat se na dar .'' maine arz kya, mazeed farmaain aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' tujhey teri Khaamiyon ka ilm , logon ko bura bhala kehney se rokey rakhey .'' ( rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( ."
4867,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Abu-Zar ! kya main tumhen do khaslatein na bataaun jo pusht par) insan ke amal ke lihaz sey) bahut halki hain jabkey meezaan mein bahut bhari hain ?'' wo bayan kartey hain, maine arz kya, ji haan ! bataeyn , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' khamosh rehna aur achey akhlaq ikhtiyar karna , us zaat ki qism jiskey haath mein meri jaan hai ! makhluq ne un jaisey do amal nahin kiye .'' ( rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( ."
4868,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) , abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas se guzrey to wo apney kisi ghulam par lanat kar rahey they aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unki taraf dekh kar farmaya : '' ( kya ( lanat karney waley aur siddiqeen ( ikhattey ho saktey hain? ( Kaba ke Rab ki qism ! hergiz nahin .'' chunanche abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne us din apney baaz ghulam ( bator kaffara ( azad kiye , phir Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aa kar arz kya : main aainda aisey nahin karunga . Imam Behaqi ne paanchon ahadis Shobil-emaan mein riwayat ki hain. ( rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( ."
4869,"Hazrat (Umar bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ke azad karda ghulam ( Aslam (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke eik roz umr (Raziallahu anhu) , abu-Bakar Siddiq (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas gaey to wo apni zaban khinch rahey they. ( ye manzar dekh kar) umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : Allah aap ki maghfirat farmaai ! usey chhod den , abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : isney mujhey halakat ke gadhon tak pahunchaya hai. rawahu Malik."
4870,"Hazrat Ubada bin Saamit (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum mujhey apni taraf se chhe chizon ki zamanat de-do to main tumhen jannat ki zamanat deta hun : jab tum baat karo to sach bolo, jab wada karo to pura karo, jab tumharey paas amanat rakhi jaey to usey ada karo, apni sharam gaahon ki hifazat karo, apni nazren neechi rakho aur apney haathon ko (zulm sey) roko.'' ( rawahu Ahmed w al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( ."
4871,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin ghanam aur Asma bint Yazid (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ke behtareen bandey wo hain ke jab unhen dekha jaey to Allah yad aa jaey, jabkey Allah ke bandon mein se bad-tareen log chughal khor, piyaaron ke darmiyan judai dalney waley aur) gunahon sey) la-talluq logon par burai ka ilzam laganey waley hain.'' (rawahu Ahmed w al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan) ."
4872,"Hazrat Abdurrehman bin ghanam aur Asma bint Yazid (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ke behtareen bandey wo hain ke jab unhen dekha jaey to Allah yad aa jaey, jabkey Allah ke bandon mein se bad-tareen log chughal khor , piyaaron ke darmiyan judai dalney waley aur) gunahon sey) la-talluq logon par burai ka ilzam laganey waley hain.'' , ( rawahu Ahmed w al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( ."
4873,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke do aadmiyon ne Zohar ya Asr ki Namaz padhi jabkey wo rozey se they, jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Namaz padh chukey to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum dono apna wuzu dobara karo, Namaz dohraao aur roza pura karo, aur kisi doosrey roz uski qaza do .'' un dono ne arz kya : Allah ke Rasool ! kyon ? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum ne falan shakhs ki gheebat ki hai.'' ( rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( ."
4874,"Hazrat abu-Saeed aur Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' gheebat zina se bhi ziyada sangeen hai? Sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya : Allah ke Rasool ! gheebat zina se kaisey ziyada sangeen hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' be-shak aadmi zina karta hai to wo tauba karta hai aur Allah uski tauba qubul farma leta hai.'' eik dusri riwayat mein hai : '' wo tauba karta hai to Allah usey bakhsh deta hai. jabkey gheebat karney waley ko maaf nahin kya jata yahan tak ke wo shakhs jiski gheebat ki gaee hai, wo usey maaf kar dey .'' ( rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan) ."
4875,"Hazrat abu-Saeed aur Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''gheebat zina se bhi ziyada sangeen hai? Sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya : Allah ke Rasool ! gheebat zina se kaisey ziyada sangeen hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' be-shak aadmi zina karta hai to wo tauba karta hai aur Allah uski tauba qubul farma leta hai.'' eik dusri riwayat mein hai : '' wo tauba karta hai to Allah usey bakhsh deta hai. jabkey gheebat karney waley ko maaf nahin kya jata yahan tak ke wo shakhs jiski gheebat ki gaee hai, wo usey maaf kar dey .'' ( rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan) ."
4876,"aur Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ki riwayat mein hai, farmaya : '' zina karney wala tauba kar leta hai jabkey gheebat karney waley ke liye tauba nahin.'' ( kyonkey wo usey ahmiyat nahin deta ke ye bhi gunah hai aur wo tauba nahin kar paata). Imam Behaqi ne teeno ahadis Shobil-emaan mein riwayat ki hain. (rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( ."
4877,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''gheebat ka kaffara ye hai ke tum ne jiski gheebat ki hai uskey liye duaaey-maghfirat karo, kaho : aey Allah ! hamari aur uski maghfirat farma .'' Behaqi fi dawaatul-kabeer . aur farmaya : iski sanad mein kamzori hai. ( rawahu al-Behaqi fi dawaatul-Kabir) ."
4878,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne wafat pai aur Ala bin Hizrami (Raziallahu anhu) ki taraf se abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas maal aaya to abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : jis shakhs ka Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) par koi qarz tha ya aapney kisi ko kuch deney ka wada farmaya tha to wo hamarey paas aaye (ham wo qarz ada karengey aur aap ka wada wafaa karengey) Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujh se wada farmaya tha ke aap mujhey is qadr aur is qadr ata farmaeyngey, aur Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne teen martaba haath phelaey, Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke unhoney lap bhar kar mujhey ata farmaya , maine unhen guna to wo paanch so they, abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : itney do baar aur lo.'' muttafaq aleh."
4879,"Hazrat abu Juhaifa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah ko) surkhi maael ( safed rangat mein dekha aur aap ke kuch baal safed ho chukey they, aur Hasan bin Ali (Raziallahu anhu) aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se mushaabihat rakhtey they, aapney hamarey liye tera oontniyon ka hukm farmaya , jab ham unhen leney gaey to aap ki wafat ki khabar hamen pahunchi chunanche hamen kuch na mil saka. albatta jab abu-Bakar ne khilaafat ki zimmedaari sanbhaali to unhoney farmaya : agar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki taraf se kisi ke paas koi ehad ho to wo tashrif laye, mein unke paas gaya aur unhen bataya to unhoney hamen oont ata karney ka hukm diya. rawahu Tirmizi."
4880,"Hazrat Abdullah bin abi hasmaa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey, aap ke aelan nabuwat se pehley koi chiz khareedi aur aap ka kuch baqaaya merey zimmey baqi reh gaya to maine aap sey, wo baqaaya usi jagah laney ka wada kya aur phir main bhool gaya, teen din baad mujhey yad aaya (aur main gaya ( to aap usi jagah par they, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum ne mujhey mashaqqat mein mubtala kar diya, mein teen din se yahan tumhara intizar kar raha hun.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
4881,"Hazrat Zaid bin Arqam (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab aadmi wada wafai ki niyat se apney bhai se koi wada kar leta hai lekin us se wada wafa nahin hua aur na wo waqt muqarrar par pahuncha to is par koi gunah nahin .'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
4882,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, eik roz meri walida ne mujhey bulaya jabkey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamarey ghar mein tashrif farma they, meri walida ne farmaya : suno, aao main tumhen kuch dungi. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen farmaya : ''tum ne usey kya deney ka irada kya hai? ''unhoney arz kya : maine usey eik khajoor deney ka irada kya hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''sun lo! agar tum usey koi chiz na detin to tumharey zimmey eik jhoot likh diya jata.'' ( rawahu Abu-Dawood w al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( ."
4883,"Hazrat Zaid bin Arqam (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ne kisi aadmi se wada kya, lekin un dono mein se eik waqt Namaz tak na aaya jabkey wo shakhs jo aa chuka tha wo Namaz padhney chala jaey to is par koi gunah nahin .'' rawahu rizeen ."
4884,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamarey sath takalluf nahin barattey they (ghul mil kar rehtey they ( yahan tak ke aap merey chhotey bhai se farmatey : abu-Umair! ''chidiyaa ne kya kya?'' abu-Umair ki eik chidiyaa thi wo uskey sath khelaa karta tha wo mar gaee . muttafaq aleh.
4885,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya : Allah ke Rasool ! aap to ham se khush tabai kar letey hain? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main haq baat hi kehta hun.'' rawahu Tirmizi ."
4886,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke eik aadmi ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se sawari talab ki to aapney farmaya : ''main tumhen oontni ke bachey par Sawar karunga.'' usney arz kya : main oontni ke bachey ko kya karunga? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''oontniyaan hi oont ko janm deti hain.'' rawahu Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood .
4887,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey farmaya : ''aey do kanon waley!'' rawahu Abu-Dawood w Tirmizi .
4888,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik budhiya aurat se farmaya : '' koi budhiya jannat mein nahin jaeygi .'' us ( aurat ( ne arz kya : unke liye kya ( maane (rukawat) ( hai? aur wo Quran padhti thi, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey farmaya : ''kya tum Quran nahin padhti ho? be-shak ham ne un ( hooron ( ko eik khas tareeqey par paida kya hai, phir unko kunwaara rakha .'' rizeen. Sharahus-sunnah mein masaabeh ke alfaz hain. (rawahu rizeen w fi Sharahus-sunnah ( ."
4889,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Zahir bin haram naami eik ganwaar shakhs jangal se Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke liye tohfey laya karta tha, aur jab wo wapsi ka irada karta to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) usey ( saman ( diya kartey they, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' zaahir jangal mein hamara kaarinda hai aur ham shehar mein uska kaam karnewaley hain.'' aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) us se mohabbat kya kartey they, halanke wo koi khoobsurat nahin tha, chunanche eik roz Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tashrif laye to wo apna saman farokht kar raha tha, aapney uskey peechey se apney gherey mein ley liya aur wo aap ko nahin dekhta tha, usney arz kya : mujhey chhod do , ye kon hai? usney eik taraf se dekha to pehchan liya ke wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hain, jab usney aap ko pehchan liya to wo badey ehtimam ke sath apni pusht Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke Sina Mubarak ke sath laganey laga , aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farmaney lagey : ''is ghulam ko kon khareedega?'' usney arz kya : Allah ke Rasool ! Allah ki qasam! meri bahut kam qeemat aap ko milegi, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''lekin tum Allah ke yahan kam qeemat ke nahin ho.'' (rawahu fi Sharahus-sunnah) ."
4890,"Hazrat Auf bin Malik Ashjai (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main ghazwa tabuk ke moqe par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua , aap chamdey ke chhotey se khemey mein they, maine salam arz kya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey salam ka jawab diya aur farmaya : '' andar aa jaao .'' maine arz kya : Allah ke Rasool ! main sara ( andar aa jaaun ( ? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum sarey ke sarey ( andar aa jaao ( .'' main andar chala gaya, Usman bin abi Aatika ( raawi ( bayan kartey hain, usney kaha : kya main chhotey se khemey mein sarey ka sara aa jaaun ? rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
4891,"Hazrat Noman bin Bashir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se aaney ki ijazat talab ki aur unhoney Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki aawaz buland hotey huey suni , jab wo andar tashrif ley aaye , to unhoney Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ko pakda ta ke unhen tamaancha maaren , aur unhoney farmaya : main tumhen Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki aawaz par aawaz buland kartey huey na dekhun . Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ko rokney lagey aur wo ghussey ki haalat mein bahar tashrif ley gaey, jab abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) bahar nikal gaey to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum ne mujhey kaisey dekha ke maine tumhen us aadmi (yani abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu)) se bachaya .'' raawi bayan kartey hain, abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) chand dino ke baad phir tashrif laye aur andar aaney ki ijazat talab ki to un dono ( Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aur Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ( ko suleh ki haalat mein paya aur unhoney un dono se kaha : tum mujhey apni suleh mein dakhil karo jaisey tum ne apni ladaai mein mujhey dakhil kya tha, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' ham kar chukey , ham kar chukey .'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
4892,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' apney ( musalman ( bhai se jhagda na kar aur na us se ( takleef deh ( mazaq na kar aur na hi us se aisa wada kar jiski to khilaf warzi karey.'' Tirmizi, aur farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi ."
4893,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se puchha gaya : logon mein se ziyada muazzaz shakhs kon hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' un mein se Allah ke yahan ziyada muazzaz shakhs wo hai jo un mein se ziyada muttaqi w perhezgar hai.'' Sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya : ham uskey mutalliq aap se nahin poochh rahey, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' tab moazzaz shakhs Yusuf (Alaihissalam) Allah ke Nabi , Allah ke Nabi ke bete , Allah ke Nabi ke potey , Allah ke khaleel ( Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) (ke padpotey hain.'' Sahaba ne arz kya : ham uskey barey mein aap se daryaft nahin kar rahey, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum Arab qabaayel ke mutalliq mujh se daryaft kar rahey ho ?'' unhoney arz kya : ji haan ! aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum mein se jo jahiliyat mein behtar they wohi tumharey Islam mein behtar hain b-sharte-ke wo ( aadaab shariyat ke mutalliq ( samajh bojh hasil karen .'' muttafaq aleh."
4894,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' karim bin karim bin karim bin karim , Yusuf bin Yaqoob bin Is-haq bin Ibrahim (Alaihimussalam) hain.'' Bukhari ."
4895,"Hazrat Bara bin Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ghazwa Hunain ke roz abu-Sufiyaan bin Haris (Raziallahu anhu) aap yani Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke khachar ki lagaam thaamey huey they, jab mushrekin ne aap ko her taraf se gher liya to aap ( sawari sey) nichey utrey aur farmaney lagey : ''main Nabi hun koi jhoot nahin, aur main abdul-Muttalib ka beta hun.'' raawi bayan kartey hain is din tamam logon mein se aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se ziyada bahadur koi nahin dekha gaya. muttafaq aleh."
4896,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, eik aadmi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to usney aap se puchha : makhluq mein se behtareen shakhsiyat ! Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' wo Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) hain.'' rawahu Muslim ."
4897,"Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''meri madah mein aisey mubaalgha na karna jaisey Nasara ne ibn Maryam ki madah mein mubaalgha se kaam liya , main to uska banda hun, tum kaho, Allah ka banda aur uska Rasool .'' muttafaq aleh."
4898,Hazrat ayaaz bin Himaar majaashi (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''be-shak Allah ne meri taraf wahi ki hai ke tum tawaazeh ikhtiyar karo yahan tak ke koi kisi par fakhr na karey aur na koi kisi par zulm karey.'' rawahu Muslim .
4899,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' log apney faut shuda baap-dada par fakhr karney se baaz aa jaeyn, wo to dozakh ke koiley hain, ya wo Allah ke yahan karam gandagi se bhi ziyada haqeer hain jo ke apni naak se ghilazat dhakelta hai, be-shak Allah ne aaba-w ijdaad par tumharey jaahili fakhr w ghurur ko khatam kar diya hai, bas wo ( fakhr karney wala ( momin muttaqi hai ya faajir bad-bakht , tamam log Adam (Alaihissalam) ki aulad hain aur Adam (Alaihissalam) mitti se ( paida huey ( hain.'' rawahu Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood ."
4900,"Hazrat Mutrif bin Abdullah bin shikhkhir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, wo (apney walid sey) bayan kartey hain, main bano Aamir ke wafad mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to ham ne arz kya : aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamarey saiyed hain. aapney farmaya : '' saiyed to Allah hai.'' phir ham ne arz kya : aap fazilat mein ham se afzal hain aur ham se azeem tar hain. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo keh rahey ho wo kaho ya apni baat ka kuch hissey kaho aur shetan tumhen ( baaten bananey par) dilair na bana dey .'' rawahu Ahmed w Abu-Dawood ."
4901,"Hazrat Hasan Basri (Raziallahu anhu) Samra (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' duniya mein izzat ki wajah maal hai jabkey Allah ke yahan ( aakhirat mein) izzat ka saman taqwa hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi w ibne-Maja ."
4902,Hazrat Ubai bin Kab (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''jo shakhs jaahili nasab ki taraf nisbat karey (aur is par fakhr karey ( to us se kaho apney baap ka aalae-tanasul kaat kar munh mein ley lo aur ye baat kinaaya se mat kaho .'' ( rawahu fi Sharahus-sunnah w Ahmed w Bukhari fi al-adabul-mufrad).
4903,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin abi Aqba (Raziallahu anhu) , abu Aqba (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain aur wo ehle Faaris ke azad karda ghulam they, unhoney kaha : main ghazwae-Uhad mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath shareek tha, maine eik mushrik par waar kya to maine kaha : usey meri taraf se wasul ( bardasht ( karo, mein Farsi nasl sey hun, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) meri taraf mutawajjeh huey aur farmaya : ''tum ne aisey kyon na kaha, usey meri taraf se wasul ( bardasht ( karo aur main Ansari , jawan hun.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
4904,"Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ne apni qom ki nahaq himayat w nusrat ki to wo us oont ki tarah hai jo kunwen mein gir jaey aur usey uski dam se pakad kar khincha jaey.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
4905,"Hazrat Waasila bin Isqaa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! asbiyat kya hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye ke tum nahaq apni qom ki muaawinat karo.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
4906,"Hazrat Suraqa bin Malik bin Jasham (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamen khutba detey huey irshad farmaya : ''tum mein se behtareen difaa karney wala wo hai jo apney khandan ka difaa karta hai b-sharte-ke wo gunah na karey.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
4907,"Hazrat Juber bin Mut-im (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' wo shakhs ham mein se nahin jisney asbiyat ki taraf bulaya , wo shakhs ham mein se nahin jo asbiyat par qitaal karey aur wo shakhs ham mein se nahin jo asbiyat par faut ho.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
4908,"Hazrat abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' kisi chiz se teri mohabbat andha aur bera bana deti hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
4909,"ehle Palestine se Ibada bin Kasir Shami apni ( filasteeni) Faseela naami aurat se riwayat kartey hain ke usney kaha, maine apney walid ko bayan kartey huey suna, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se masla daryaft kartey huey arz kya : Allah ke Rasool ! kya ye bhi asbiyat mein aata hai ke aadmi apni qom se mohabbat karey ? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' nahin, balke asbiyat to ye hai ke aadmi apni qom ki nahaq himayat w nusrat karey.'' rawahu Ahmed w ibne-Maja ."
4910,"Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tumharey ye ansab ( zaat , qabiley ( kisi ke liye baais aar nahin, tum sab Adam ki aulad ho aur tum sab baham (aapas mein) is tarah barabar ho jis tarah eik saa doosrey saa ke barabar hota hai, Deen aur taqwa ke ilawa kisi ko kisi par koi fazilat nahin, aadmi ke liye aar ke lihaz se yehi kafi hai ke wo zaban daraz , fohsh bhale hi aur bakheel ho.'' , ( rawahu Ahmed w al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( ."
4911,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, kisi aadmi ne arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! merey husne-suluk ka sab se ziyada haq daar kon hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' teri walida .'' usney arz kya : phir kon ? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' teri maa .'' usney arz kya : phir kon ? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' teri maa .'' usney arz kya : phir kon ? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' tera baap .'' eik dusri riwayat mein hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' teri maa , phir teri maa , phir teri maa , phir tera baap , phir tera qaribi rishte-dar , phir us se kam qaribi rishte-dar .'' muttafaq aleh."
4912,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' uski naak khaak aalud ho, uski naak khaak aalud ho, uski naak khaak aalud ho ! '' arz kya gaya : Allah ke Rasool ! kis ki ? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo apney waliden mein se kisi eik ko ya dono ko budhapey mein pa ley phir wo ( unke sath husne-suluk karkey ( jannat mein dakhil na ho.'' rawahu Muslim ."
4913,"Hazrat Asma binte-abi Bakr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan karti hain, meri walida merey paas tashrif laain jabkey wo mushrika thi, ye us waqt ki baat hai jab Quraish se ( Hudebiya ka ( muahida hua tha, maine arz kya : Allah ke Rasool ! be-shak meri walida merey paas aai hain jabkey wo behtar sulook ki mutmanni hai to kya main us se sila rehmi karun ? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''haan! us se sila rehmi karo.'' muttafaq aleh."
4914,"Hazrat Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''aale-abu falan merey dost w himayati nahin, mera himayati to Allah aur Saleh momin hain, lekin unke sath rishta daari hai jisey mein sila rehmi ke zariey barqarar rakhunga.'' muttafaq aleh."
4915,"Hazrat Mughira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''be-shak Allah ne maaon ki nafarmani karney , betiyon ko zinda dargor kerney, bukhl karney aur sawal key liye hath phailaney ko tum par haram qarar diya hai, aur fuzul baaten kerney, ( logon ke ahwaal janney ke liye ( ziyada sawal karney aur maal zaya karney ko tumharey mutalliq napasand farmaya hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
4916,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aadmi ka apney waliden ko gaali dena bada gunah hai.'' Sahaba ne arz kya, Allah ke Rasool! kya aadmi apney waliden ko gaali deta hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' haan , wo kisi aadmi ke walid ko gaali deta hai to ( badley mein) wo uskey walid ko gaali deta hai, aur ye uski maa ko gaali deta hai, to ( badley mein) wo uski maa ko gaali deta hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
4917,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' be-shak aadmi ka apney walid ke faut ho janey ke baad , uskey doston se sila rehmi karna sab se badi neki hai.'' rawahu Muslim ."
4918,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs ye pasand karta hai ke uska rizq faraakh kar diya jaey aur uski umr daraz kar di jaey to wo sila rehmi karey.'' muttafaq aleh."
4919,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ne makhluq ko paida farmaya , aur jab wo us se farigh hua to rehem khada ho gaya aur usney Rehman ki kamar pakad li, is par (Rehman) ne farmaya : hat ja? us ( rehem ( ne arz kya, ye maqam uska hai jo terey sath qata rehmi se panah talab karta hai, farmaya : kya tum is par razi nahin ke main us se talluq qaaim rakhun jo tujh se talluq qaaim rakhey, aur jo tujh se talluq tod dey mein us se talluq tod dun, rehem ne arz kya, rab ji ! kyon nahin (main razi hun) , farmaya : ''ye maine jo kaha aisey hi hoga .'' muttafaq aleh."
4920,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''reham, Rehman se mushtaq hai, Allah ne farmaya : ''jisney tujh se talluq qaaim kya main us se talluq qaaim karunga aur jisney tujh se talluq toda mein us se talluq tod dunga.'' Bukhari ."
4921,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' rehem arsh ke sath muallaq hai, wo arz karta hai : jisney mujhey joda Allah usey jodey aur jisney mujhey toda Allah usey todey .'' muttafaq aleh."
4922,"Hazrat Juber bin Mut-im (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''qata rehmi karney (rishtey katney) wala jannat mein nahin jaeyga.'' muttafaq aleh."
4923,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''sila rehmi ke badley mein sila rehmi karney wala, sila rehmi karney wala nahin, balke sila rehmi karney wala to wo hai ke jab uskey sath qata' rehmi ki jaey to wo sila rehmi karey.'' Bukhari ."
4924,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke eik aadmi ne arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! merey kuch rishtedaar hain, main un se sila rehmi karta hun aur wo mujh se qata rehmi kartey hain, main un se husne-suluk karta hun aur wo mujh se bad-suluki kartey hain, main un se darguzar karta hun aur wo mujh par ziyadti kartey hain. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar tumhara bayan durust hai to phir tum unke munh mein garm raakh dal rahey ho, jab tak tum us rawish par qaaim rahogey to unke khilaf Allah ki taraf se tumhen madad pahunchti rahegi .'' rawahu Muslim ."
4925,"Hazrat Soban (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''dua, taqdir ko badal deti hai, husne-suluk se umr mein izafa ho jata hai, be-shak aadmi gunah ke irtikab ki wajeh se rizq se mehroom kar diya jata hai.'' rawahu ibne-Maja ."
4926,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main jannat mein dakhil hua to maine wahan qirat suni to maine kaha : ye kon (qirat kar raha) hai? unhoney kaha : Harisa bin Noman hain, husne-suluk ki yehi jaza hoti hai, husne-suluk ki jaza aisi hi hoti hai.'' aur wo apni walida ke sath sab se badh kar husne-suluk karney waley they. Behaqi ne usey Shobil-emaan mein riwayat kya hai aur eik riwayat mein hai : ''main jannat mein dakhil hua '' ki bajaey ''maine khuwab mein apney aap ko jannat mein dekha .'' ke alfaz hain. ( rawahu fi Sharahus-sunnah w al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( ."
4927,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''walid razi to rab razi, walid naraz to rab naraz.'' rawahu Tirmizi ."
4928,"Hazrat abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke eik aadmi uskey paas aaya to usney kaha : meri eik biwi hai, jabkey meri walida usey Talaq deney ka mujhey hukm deti hai, (ye sun kar) abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) ne usey kaha, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : '' walid jannat ka behtareen darwaza hai, agar tum chaho to darwazey ki hifazat kar lo, aur chaho to zaya kar lo .'' rawahu Tirmizi w ibne-Maja ."
4929,"Hazrat Behaz bin Hakim apney walid se aur wo apney dada se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha : maine arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! main kis se husne-suluk karun ? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' apni maa se .'' maine arz kya, phir kon ? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' apni walida ke sath .'' maine arz kya, phir kon ? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' apni maa ke sath .'' maine arz kya, phir kon ? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' apni maa ke sath .'' maine arz kya, phir kis ke sath ? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' apney walid ke sath , phir qarib tareen aur phir qarib tar rishtedar ke sath (achcha sulook kar).'' rawahu Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood ."
4930,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Auf (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''Allah tabarak w taala farmata hai : main Allah hun aur main Rehman hun, maine rehem takhleeq kya aur uska naam apney naam (Rehman) se tajwiz kya, jisney usey joda mein usey jodunga aur jisney usey toda main usey (apni rehmat sey) mehroom kar dunga .'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
4931,"Hazrat Abdullah bin abi Aufi (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''jis qom mein qata' rehmi karney wala shakhs ho is par rehmat nazil nahin hoti.'' ( rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( ."
4932,"Hazrat abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''zulm w sarkashi aur qata-rehmi aisey gunah hain ke unke murtakib ko Allah duniya mein saza deney ke sath-sath usey aakhirat mein bhi zakhira kar leta hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood ."
4933,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' ehsan jatlaaney wala, waliden ka nafarman aur mustaqil sharab nosh jannat mein nahin jaeyga.'' rawahu Nasai w Darmi ."
4934,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''apney nasab ko is qadr zarur seekho jiskey mutabiq tum sila rehmi kartey ho, kyonkey sila rehmi ehle rehem mein mohabbat, maal mein izaafey aur daraazie-Umar ka baais hai.'' Tirmizi, aur farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
4935,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke eik aadmi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to usney arz kya : Allah ke Rasool ! maine eik bahut badey gunah ka irtikab kya hai to kya merey liye tauba (ki gunjaaish) hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya tumhari walida hai?'' usney arz kya, nahin, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya tumhari khaala hai? '' usney arz kya : ji haan! aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' uskey sath husne-suluk karo.'' rawahu Tirmizi ."
4936,"Hazrat abu-Usaid Saaidi (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, is beech mein ke ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir they ke itney mein bano Salma (ke qabiley ( se eik aadmi aap ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur usney arz kya : Allah ke Rasool ! kya waliden ke sath husne-suluk ki koi aisi surat hai jiskey zariey mein unki wafat ke baad un se husne-suluk kar sakun ? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' haan ! unke liye dua karo, unke liye maghfirat talab karo, unke baad unki wasiyat par amal karo, wo jo sila rehmi kya kartey they usey jari rakho aur unke doston ki takrim karo.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood w ibne-Maja."
4937,"Hazrat abu-Tufail (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko Jaaraana ke maqam par gosht taqseem kartey huey dekha, achcha eik aurat aai yahan tak ke wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke qarib ho gaee aur aapney uskey liye apni chadar bicha di aur wo is par beth gaee . maine puchha ye kon hai? to unhoney bataya : ye aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki razaaii walida hain. rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
4938,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' us doran ke teen aadmi safar kar rahey they, barish aa gaee , unhoney pahad main eik ghaar mein panah li , itney mein pahad se eik chattan giri aur usney unki ghaar ka munh band kar diya. chunanche unhoney eik doosrey se kaha : apney aamaal ka jayeza lo jo tum ne khalis Allah ki raza ki khatir kiye they, phir unke zariey Allah se dua karo shayad ke wo us takleef ( chattan ( ko door kar dey , un mein se eik ne kaha : aey Allah ! merey boodhey waliden they aur merey chhotey chhotey bachey they, mein unke naan w nafqa ka zimmedar tha, jab main Sham ke waqt maweshi lekar wapis aata to main doodh doh kar , apni aulad se pehley , apney waliden ki khidmat mein pesh kya karta tha, eik martaba mein jangal mein door nikal gaya jiski wajeh se main Sham ke waqt ( der sey) ghar pahuncha to maine un dono ko soyaa hua paya , maine hasbe-mamool doodh doha, phir main doodh ka bartan lekar aaya aur unke sarhaaney khada ho gaya, maine unhen jagana munasib na samjha aur un se pehley bachon ko pilaanaa bhi na-munasib jana jabkey bachey merey qadmon ke paas bhookey bilaktey rahey, meri aur unki yehi soorate-haal rahi yahan tak ke subh ho gaee, (aey Allah!) agar to janta hai ke maine teri raza ki khatir aisey kya tha to phir hamarey liye is qadr raasta bana dey ke ham wahan se aasman dekh lein, Allah ne unke liye raasta khol diya yahan tak ke wo aasman dekhney lagey. doosrey ne arz kya, aey Allah! meri eik chacha zaad behan thi, main usey itna chahta tha jitna ke ziyada se ziyada mard khawatin ko chahtey hain, maine us se burai karney ka irada zahir kya lekin usney inkar kar diya, yahan tak ke main usey so Dinar dun, maine koshish karkey so Dinar jama kiye aur wo lekar uskey paas gaya, aur jab main (us se bura kaam karney ke liye ( uski dono taangon ke darmiyan beth gaya to usney kaha : Allah ke bandey ! Allah se dar ja aur us mehar ko na tod , ( ye suntey hi ( main us se uth khada hua. aey Allah ! agar to janta hai ke maine ye teri raza ki khatir kya tha to hamarey liye raasta khol dey! Allah ne unke liye kuch raasta khol diya. teesrey shakhs ne kaha : aey Allah ! maine eik farq chaawalon ki ujrat par eik mazdoor kaam par laga rakha tha, pas jab usney apna kaam mukammal kar liya to usney kaha : mera haq mujhey ada karo, jab maine uska haq is par pesh kya to wo usey kamtar samajhtey huey chhod kar chala gaya mein us se kheti karta raha yahan tak ke maine us se gaey aur charwahey jama kar liye , wo merey paas aaya aur usney kaha : Allah se dar ja aur mujh par zulm na kar aur mera haq mujhey ada kar , maine kaha ye gaaey aur uskey charaney waley ko ley ja , usney kaha : Allah se dar ! mujh se mazaq na kar , maine kaha : main tum se mazaq nahin kar raha , tum ye gaey aur uskey charwahey ko ley jaao , wo usey lekar chala gaya. agar to janta hai ke maine ye kaam teri raza hasil karney ke liye kya tha to baqi raasta bhi khol dey , chunanche Allah ne unke liye raasta khol diya (aur wo takleef door kar di ( .'' muttafaq aleh."
4939,"Hazrat Muawiya bin Jahma se riwayat hai ke Jahma (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaye aur unhoney arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! main jihad mein shareek honey ke liye aap se mashwara karna chahta hun, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya tumhari walida hai? '' usney arz kya : ji haan ! aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' jaao ! uskey paas raho , kyonkey jannat uskey qadmon ke paas hai.'' , ( rawahu Ahmed w Nasai w al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( ."
4940,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, meri eik biwi thi jisey main pasand karta tha, jabkey umr (Raziallahu anhu) usey napasand kartey they, unhoney mujhey farmaya : ''usey Talaq dey do , maine inkar kar diya to umr (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur aap se ye waqia bayan kya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey farmaya : ''usey Talaq dey do.'' rawahu Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood ."
4941,Hazrat abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke kisi aadmi ne arz kya : Allah ke Rasool ! waliden ka apni aulad par kya haq hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' dono tumhari jannat (ka sabab ( hain aur tumhari jahannam (ka sabab ( hain.'' rawahu ibne-Maja .
4942,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' eik bandey ke waliden ya un dono mein se eik faut ho jata hai jabkey wo un dono ka nafarman hota hai, aur wo ( unki maut ke baad) unke liye dua karta rehta hai aur un dono ke liye maghfirat talab karta rehta hai to Allah aisey shakhs ko husne-suluk karney wala likh deta hai.'' ( rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( ."
4943,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs apney waliden (ke haq) ke mutalliq Allah ki itaat mein subh karta hai to uskey liye jannat ke darwazey khul jatey hain aur agar eik ho to ( darwaza bhi) eik , aur jo shakhs apney waliden (ke haq (ke mutalliq Allah ki nafarmani mein subh karta hai to uskey liye jahannam ke darwazey khul jatey hain, aur agar wo eik ho to ( jahannam ka darwaza bhi) eik.'' eik aadmi ne arz kya, bhale hi wo is par zulm keren? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar-che wo is par zulm karen, agar-che wo is par zulm karen aur agar-che wo is par zulm keren.'' ( rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( ."
4944,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' nek bacha jab apney waliden ko nazar rehmat se dekhta hai to Allah uskey her baar dekhney ke badley main, uskey liye hajje-mabroor ka sawab likh deta hai.'' Sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya : agar-che wo her roz so martaba dekhey ? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' haan , Allah ( tasawwur sey) bahut bada aur) her naqs sey) paak tar hai.'' , ( rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( ."
4945,"Hazrat abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' waliden ki nafarmani ke ilawa Allah jitney chahey gunah maaf kar deta hai, kyonkey wo us ( gunah (ke murtakib ko marney se pehley zindagi hi mein saza dey deta hai.'' ( rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( ."
4946,"Hazrat Saeed bin Aas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' badey bhai ka apney chhotey bhaiyon par aisey haq hai jaisey walid ka apni aulad par haq hai.'' Imam Behaqi ne paanchon ahadis Shobil-emaan mein riwayat ki hain. ( rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( ."
4947,"Hazrat Jarir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah us shakhs par rehem nahin farmata jo logon par rehem nahin karta .'' muttafaq aleh."
4948,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, eik eraabi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to usney puchha : kya aap bachon ka bosa letey hain? jabkey ham to unka bosa nahin letey , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main tumharey mutalliq ikhtiyar nahin rakhta jabkey Allah ne terey dil se rehmat nikal di hai, (ke main usey wapis la sakun) .'' muttafaq aleh."
4949,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, eik aurat merey paas aai aur uskey sath uski do betiyan bhi thin, usney mujh se sawal kya, merey paas sirf eik khajoor hi thi, maine wohi usey de-di , usney usey apni dono betiyon ke darmiyan taqseem kar diya, aur khud na khai , phir wo khadi hui aur chali gaee . Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) merey paas tashrif laye to maine aap se uska tazkira kya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ki un betiyon se kisi tarah aazmaaish ki gaee aur usney un se husne-suluk kya to wo uskey liye jahannam se aad bin jaeyngi.'' muttafaq aleh."
4950,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ne do bachchiyon ki parwarish ki yahan tak ke wo baligh ho gaeen to wo roze-qiyamat is tarah aaeyga ke main aur wo is tarah hongey .'' aur aapney apni ungliyan milaain . rawahu Muslim ."
4951,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''bewa aur miskeen ki zarooraton ka khayal rakhney wala, Allah ki raah mein jihad karney waley ki tarah hai.'' aur mera khayal hai ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''wo qiyam karney ( tahajjud padhney ( waley ki tarah hai jo susti nahin karta, aur us roze daar ki tarah hai jo iftaar nahin karta ( musalsal rozey rakhta hai) .'' muttafaq aleh."
4952,"Hazrat Sehal bin Saad (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main aur yateem ki kafalat karney wala, chahe yateem uska apna ho ya kisi aur ka, jannat mein is tarah hongey.'' aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne angusht shahadat aur darmiyani ungli ke sath ishara farmaya aur phir un dono ( ungliyon (ke darmiyan kuch farq kya. Bukhari ."
4953,"Hazrat Noman bin Bashir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' aap mominon ko baham (aapas mein) rehmat w meharbani kerney, baham (aapas mein) mohabbat aur muaawinat karney mein, jism ki manind paeyngey, jab koi uzu takleef mein mubtala hota hai to uski wajeh se uska sara jism bedaari aur bukhar mein mubtala rehta hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
4954,"Hazrat Noman bin Bashir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tamam momin fard wahid ki tarah hain, agar uski aankh dukhti hai to uska sara jism dukhata hai, aur agar uska sar takleef mein mubtala hota hai to bhi uska sara jism takleef mehsus karta hai.'' rawahu Muslim ."
4955,"Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''momin (doosrey) momin ke liye imarat ki manind hai, jis ka eik hissey doosrey hissey ko mazbut karta hai.'' phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik haath ki ungliyan doosrey haath ki ungliyon mein dalin. muttafaq aleh."
4956,"Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain ke jab saail ya koi zarurat mand shakhs aap ke paas aata to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farmatey : ''tum ( mujh sey) sifarish karo tumhen ajr milega, aur Allah jo chahega wo apney Rasool ki zaban par jari farma dega.'' muttafaq aleh."
4957,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''apney (musalman) bhai ki madad karo, wo zalim ho ya mazloom.'' kisi aadmi ne arz kya : Allah ke Rasool! main mazloom ki to madad karunga lekin zalim ki madad kaisey karun? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tumhara usey zulm se rokna, yehi tumhara uski madad karna hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
4958,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''musalman musalman ka bhai hai na to wo is par zulm karta hai aur na usey ( zalim ke) supurd karta hai aur jo shakhs apney bhai ki hajat puri karney mein laga ho to Allah uski hajat puri farmata hai, aur jo shakhs kisi musalman ki koi pareshani door karta hai to Allah us se qiyamat ke roz ki pareshaniyon mein se koi pareshani door farma dega, aur jo shakhs kisi musalman ki parda poshi karta hai to roze-qiyamat Allah uski parda poshi farmaeyga.'' muttafaq aleh."
4959,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''musalman musalman ka bhai hai wo na is par zulm karta hai aur na usey be yaar w madadgar chhodta hai aur na hi usey haqeer khayal karta hai, taqwa yahan hai.'' aur aapney apney seeney ki taraf teen martaba ishara kya, kisi aadmi ke bura honey ke liye yehi kafi hai ke wo apney musalman bhai ko haqeer khayal karey, her musalman ka khoon, uska maal aur uski izzat doosrey musalman par haram hai.'' rawahu Muslim ."
4960,"Hazrat ayaaz bin Himaar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' ehle jannat teen qism ke hain : munsif , khairat karney wala aur neki karney ki tofiq se nawaza gaya badshah, ( doosra ( her rishtedar se ( khususan (aur her musalman se ( umuman ( meharbani aur naram dili ke jazbaat rakhney wala shakhs aur) teesra ( ayaal daar jo ke haram chizon aur sawal karney se ijtinab karta hai. jabkey jahannamiyon ki paanch qismein hain : wo zaeef jis mein aql nahin (jiskey zariey wo buri baat se bachey), wo log jo tumharey matehet hain, jinhen (halal) ehel w ayaal aur maal ki khaahish nahin, khaain shakhs ke agar uskey dil mein kisi maamuli si chiz ka tama (lalach) paida ho to wo uski khayanat kar leta hai, wo aadmi jo subh w Sham (her moqe par) terey ehl w ayaal aur terey maal ke barey mein tujh se dhoka karta hai.'' aur aapney bakheel ya jhootey ka zikr kya. ''aur bad-akhlaq jo fohsh bhale hi ho.'' rawahu Muslim ."
4961,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''us zaat ki qism jiskey haath mein meri jaan hai! koi banda us waqt tak momin nahin ho sakta jab tak wo apney bhai ke liye wohi chiz pasand na karey jo wo apney liye pasand karta hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
4962,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ki qasam! wo momin nahin, Allah ki qism ! wo momin nahin, Allah ki qasam! wo momin nahin.'' arz kya gaya : Allah ke Rasool! kon (momin nahin)? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jiski shararaton se uska padosi mehfooz nahin.'' muttafaq aleh."
4963,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''wo shakhs, jiski shar-angeziyon se uska padosi mehfooz na ho wo jannat mein nahin jaeyga.'' rawahu Muslim."
4964,"Hazrat Aaisha aur ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Jibrael (Alaihissalam) padosi ke mutalliq mujhey musalsal wasiyat kartey rahey yahan tak ke maine khayal kya ke wo usey waris bana dengey.'' muttafaq aleh."
4965,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum teen ho to teesrey ko chhod kar do eik doosrey se sargoshi na karen yahan tak ke tum logon ke sath mil jaao, uskey liye ye tarze-amal us (teesrey shakhs) ko gham mein mubtala kar dega.'' muttafaq aleh."
4966,"Hazrat Tameem daari (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne teen martaba farmaya : ''deen, ikhlas w khair khaahi (ka naam) hai.'' ham ne arz kya, kis ke liye? farmaya : ''Allah ke liye, uski kitab ke liye, uskey Rasool ke liye, musalmanon ke hukmranon ke liye aur aam musalmanon ke liye .'' rawahu Muslim ."
4967,"Hazrat Jarir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Namaz qaaim kerney, Zakat ada karney aur her musalman ke sath khair-khahi karney par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki baiat ki . muttafaq aleh."
4968,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine abul-Qaasim (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''kisi bad-naseeb shakhs hi se rehmat salb ki jati hai.'' rawahu Ahmed w Tirmizi ."
4969,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' rehem karney walon par Rehman rehem farmata hai, zamin walon par tum rehem karo, aasman wala tum par rehem farmaeyga .'' rawahu Abu-Dawood w Tirmizi ."
4970,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs hamarey chhoton par rehem nahin karta aur hamarey badon ki tauqeer nahin karta , neki ka hukm nahin karta aur na wo burai se rokta hai, wo ham mein se nahin .'' Tirmizi, aur unhoney farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi ."
4971,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo nojawan kisi umr raseeda (badi umr key) shakhs ki uskey umr raseeda honey ki wajeh se izzat karta hai to Allah uskey umr raseeda honey par aisa shakhs mutayyan farmaeyga jo uski izzat kerega .'' rawahu Tirmizi ."
4972,"Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''boodhey musalman ki izzat karna , aisey Hafiz Quran ki izzat karna jo ghulu se kaam na leta ho aur aadil badshah ki izzat karna Allah ki azmat se hai.'' , ( rawahu Abu-Dawood w al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( ."
4973,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' musalmanon ke gharon mein se wo ghar behtar hai jis mein koi yateem ho aur uskey sath achcha suluk kya jata ho, aur musalmanon ka wo ghar bura hai jis mein koi yateem ho aur uskey sath bura sulook kya jata ho.'' rawahu ibne-Maja ."
4974,"Hazrat abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs Allah ki raza ki khatir kisi yateem ke sar par (shafqat sey) haath phertaa hai to uskey haath ke nichey aaney waley her baal ke badley mein usey eik neki milti hai, aur jo shakhs apney zere-kafalat kisi yateem bachi ya bachey ke sath achcha suluk karta hai to wo aur main jannat mein is tarah hongey.'' aur aapney apni dono ungliyan milaain. Ahmed, Tirmizi, aur farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Ahmed w Tirmizi."
4975,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs kisi yateem ko apney khaney peeney ( dasterkhaan ( mein shareek karta hai to Allah uskey liye lazimi taur par jannat wajib kar deta hai, b-sharte-ke usney koi naaqaabile-maafi gunah na kya ho, aur jo shakhs teen betiyon ya itni hi behnon ki kafalat karta hai aur unki achi tarbiyat karta hai, un par rehem karta hai yahan tak ke wo unki tamam zarooratein puri kar deta hai to Allah us shakhs ke liye jannat wajib kar deta hai.'' kisi aadmi ne arz kya : Allah ke Rasool! kya do (ki kafalat karney wala) bhi ? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''haan wo bhi.'' yahan tak ke agar wo kehtey, kya eik bhi? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farma detey : eik bhi.'' aur Allah jis shakhs ki do umda chizen salb kar ley to uskey liye jannat wajib ho gaee.'' arz kya gaya : Allah ke Rasool! do umda chizon se kya murad hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''uski do aankhen.'' ( rawahu fi Sharahus-sunnah ( ."
4976,"Hazrat Jabir bin Samra (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aadmi ka apney bachey ki achi tarbiyat karna uskey liye eik saa sadqa karney se behtar hai.'' Tirmizi, aur unhoney farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai, aur naaseh raawi as-haabul hadees ke yahan qawi nahin. rawahu Tirmizi ."
4977,"Hazrat Ayub bin Musa apney walid se aur wo apney dada se riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''waliden apni aulad ko jo behtareen Atiya deta hai wo unki achi tarbiyat hai.'' Tirmizi, Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan. aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : merey nazdik ye hadees mursal hai. (rawahu Tirmizi w al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan) ."
4978,"Hazrat Auf bin Malik Ashjai (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main aur siyah rukhsaaron wali aurat ( wo bewa jiskey chehrey ka rang mehnat mazduri karney ki wajeh se siyah ho gaya ( roze-qiyamat is tarah hongey.'' aur Yazid bin Zaree ne darmiyani ungli aur shahadat ki ungli ki taraf ishara kya.'' neez mansab w jamaal wali aurat jiska khawind faut ho jaey aur wo apney yateem bachon ki wajeh se shaadi na karey yahan tak ke wo badey ho jaeyn ya faut ho jaeyn.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
4979,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ki beti ho aur wo usey zinda dafn na karey aur na uski tauheen karey aur na hi wo apney bete ko is par tarjeeh dey to Allah usey jannat mein dakhil farmaeyga .'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
4980,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ke paas uskey musalman bhai ki gheebat ki jaey aur wo uski nusrat w difaa par qadir ho aur usney uska difaa kya to Allah duniya w aakhirat mein uski nusrat w difaa farmaeyga agar wo uski nusrat par qadir honey ke bawajud uski nusrat nahin karta to Allah duniya w aakhirat mein usey be yaar w madadgar chhod dega.'' zaeef, (rawahu fi Sharahus-sunnah) ."
4981,"Hazrat Asma binte-Yazid (Raziallahu anhu) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jisney apney (musalman) bhai ki ghair mojudgi mein uski gheebat na honey di to Allah par haq hai ke wo usey jahannam ki aag se azad kar dey.'' ( rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( ."
4982,"Hazrat abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''jo musalman apney kisi musalman bhai ki izzat ka difaa karta hai to Allah par haq hai ke wo roze-qiyamat uska jahannam se difaa karey.'' phir aapney ye aayat tilawat farmaai : '' mominon ki madad karna ham par lazim hai.'' ( rawahu fi Sharahus-sunnah ( ."
4983,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo koi musalman kisi musalman ko kisi aisi jagah tanha chhod dey jahan uski be hurmati aur be izzati ki ja rahi ho to Allah us shakhs ko aisi jagah tanha , be yaar w madadgar chhod dega jahan wo madad ka mohtaj hoga, aur agar koi musalman kisi musalman ki kisi aisi jagah madad karta hai jahan uski be izzati aur be hurmati ki jati ho to Allah aisi jagah uski madad farmaeyga jahan wo pasand karta ho ke uski nusrat ho.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
4984,"Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jisney (kisi ka ( koi aeb dekha aur uski parda poshi ki to wo us shakhs ki tarah hai jisney zinda dargor ko zinda kya.'' Ahmed, Tirmizi, aur unhoney usey sahih qarar diya. rawahu Ahmed w Tirmizi ."
4985,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''be-shak tum mein se her eik apney (musalman ( bhai ke liye aaina hai, agar wo is mein koi aeb dekhey to wo us se zaayel kar dey.'' Tirmizi, aur unhoney usey zaeef qarar diya hai. Tirmizi aur Abu-Dawood ki riwayat mein hai : '' momin momin ka aaina hai, aur momin momin ka bhai hai, wo uska nuqsan nahin honey deta aur wo uski ghair mojudgi mein us (ke jaan w maal aur izzat ( ki hifazat karta hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi, . Hasan rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
4986,"Hazrat Muaz bin Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs kisi momin ki izzat kisi munafiq se bachata hai to Allah eik farishta bhejega jo roze-qiyamat uskey gosht ko jahannam ki aag se bachaeyga, aur jisney kisi musalman shakhs par usko badnaam karney ke liye koi tohmat lagai to Allah usko jahannam ke pul par rok lega yahan tak ke wo ( saza bhugat kar) apni kahi hui baat se paak ho jaey.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
4987,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ke nazdik behtareen sathi wo hai jo un mein apney sathi ke liye behtar hai aur Allah ke nazdik behtareen padosi wo hai jo apney padosi ke liye behtar hai.'' Tirmizi, Darmi , aur Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi w Darmi ."
4988,"Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, eik aadmi ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se arz kya : Allah ke Rasool ! mujhey kaisey pata chaley ke main achcha hun ya bura ? Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum apney padausiyon ko kehtey huey suno ke tum achey ho to tum achey ho aur jab tum unhen kehtey huey suno ke tum burey ho to tum burey ho.'' rawahu ibne-Maja ."
4989,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' logon se unke maqam w martabey ke mutabiq bartaw karo.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood .
4990,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin abi Quraad (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik roz wuzu farmaya to aap ke Sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) aap ke wuzu ke pani ko jismon par malney lagey to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen farmaya : '' kis chiz ne tumhen is par aamada kya ?'' unhoney arz kya : Allah aur uskey Rasool ki mohabbat ne, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs ye pasand karta ho ke wo Allah aur uskey Rasool se mohabbat karey ya Allah aur uskey Rasool usey pasand farmaain to wo jab baat karey sach boley , jab uskey paas amanat rakhi jaey to usey ada karey aur apney padosiyon aur meil-jol rakhney walon se husne-suluk karey.'' ( rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( ."
4991,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''wo shakhs momin nahin jo pet bhar kar khaye jabkey uska qaribi hamsaaya bhooka ho.'' Imam Behaqi ne dono hadisein Shobil-emaan mein riwayat ki hain. (rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan)."
4992,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, eik aadmi ne arz kya : Allah ke Rasool! falan aurat apni namazon, rozon aur sadqaat ki kasrat ke hawaley se mashhoor hai lekin wo apni zaban darazi se apney padosiyon ko takleef pahunchati hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' wo jahannami hai.'' usney arz kya : Allah ke Rasool ! falan aurat apni namazon , rozon aur sadqaat ki qillat ke hawaley se mashhoor hai, aur wo paneer ke chand tukdey sadqa karti hai aur wo apni zaban darazi ke zariey apney padosiyon ko takleef nahin pahunchati, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''wo jannati hai.'' (rawahu Ahmed w al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan)."
4993,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) chand aisey logon ke paas, khadey huey jo bethey huey they to farmaya : ''kya main tumhen tumharey burey aur achey logon ke mutalliq na bataaun ?'' raawi bayan kartey hain, wo khamosh rahey, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne teen martaba aisey farmaya , to eik aadmi ne arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! kyon nahin, aap hamarey burey mein se behtar ke mutalliq hamen zarur bataeyn . aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum mein se behtar shakhs wo hai jis se khair ki tawaqqo ki jaey aur uskey shar se aman ho jabkey tum mein se bura wo hai jis se khair ki tawaqqo na ki jaey aur uskey shar se aman na ho.'' Tirmizi, Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan , aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. ( rawahu Tirmizi w al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( ."
4994,"Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' be-shak Allah Taala ne tumharey darmiyan tumharey akhlaq taqseem kiye hain jis tarah usney tumharey amwaal taqseem kiye hain, be-shak Allah Taala her shakhs ko duniya ata karta hai chahey wo shakhs usey pasand ho ya napasand jabkey wo Deen sirf usey ata karta hai jisey pasand farmata hai, jis shakhs ko Allah Deen ata farma dey to ( samjho ke) wo Allah ka pasandida shakhs hai, us zaat ki qism jiskey haath mein meri jaan hai ! koi banda musalman nahin ho sakta jab tak ke uska dil aur uski zaban musalman nahin ho jatey , aur wo us waqt tak momin nahin hota jab tak uska padosi uski shararaton se mehfooz na ho jaey.'' (rawahu Ahmed w al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( ."
4995,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' momin ulfat ka maskan (sarasar ulfat) hai, aur us shakhs mein koi khair nahin jo kisi se ulfat nahin karta aur na us se koi ulfat karta hai.'' Ahmed, aur Imam Behaqi ne dono ahadis Shobil-emaan mein bayan ki hain. ( rawahu Ahmed w al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( ."
4996,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jisney merey kisi ummati ki zarurat puri ki jiskey zariey wo usey khush karna chahta ho to usney mujhey khush kya, jisney mujhey khush kya to usney Allah ko khush kya, aur jisney Allah ko khush kya to Allah usey jannat mein dakhil farmaeyga .'' ( rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( ."
4997,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo kisi musibat zada shakhs ki fariyad rasi karta hai to Allah uskey liye 73 maghfiratein likh deta hai, un mein se eik mein uskey tamam maamlat ki durusti hai jabkey 72 roze-qiyamat uskey liye darjaat ke husool ka baais hongi .'' ( rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( ."
4998,"Hazrat Anas aur Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' makhluq Allah ki ayaal ( zer kafalat ( hai, aur makhluq mein se wo shakhs Allah ko ziyada pasand hai jo uski ayaal se achcha suluk karta hai.'' Imam Behaqi ne teeno ahadis Shobil-emaan mein bayan ki hain. ( rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( ."
4999,"Hazrat Anas aur Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' makhluq Allah ki ayaal ( zer kafalat ( hai, aur makhluq mein se wo shakhs Allah ko ziyada pasand hai jo uski ayaal se achcha suluk karta hai.'' Imam Behaqi ne teeno ahadis Shobil-emaan mein bayan ki hain. ( rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan )."
5000,"Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' roze-qiyamat sab se pehley do padausiyon ka muqadma pesh hoga .'' rawahu Ahmed ."
5001,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke kisi aadmi ne apni sang dili ki Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se shikayat ki to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''yateem ke sar par daste-shafqat phera kar aur miskeen ko khana khilaya kar .'' rawahu Ahmed .
5002,Hazrat Suraqa bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya main tumhen behtareen sadqe ke mutalliq na bataaun?'' wo teri is beti par sadqa karna hai jo ( Talaq waghera ki wajeh sey) terey paas lot aaye aur terey siwa uskey liye kamaaney wala bhi na ho.'' rawahu ibne-Maja .
5003,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' roohen mukhtalif qism ke lashkar hain jo baham (aapas mein) mutaarif hoti hain wo duniya mein baham (aapas mein) mohabbat se rehti hain, aur jin mein ajnabiyat thi un mein ikhtilaf rehta hai.'' Bukhari ."
5004,aur Imam Muslim (Raziallahu anhu) ne usey Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kya hai. rawahu Muslim .
5005,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' be-shak jab Allah kisi bandey se mohabbat karta hai to wo Jibrael (Alaihissalam) ko bula kar farmata hai : be-shak main falan shakhs se mohabbat karta hun lihaza tum bhi us se mohabbat karo, farmaya : Jibrael (Alaihissalam) us se mohabbat kartey hain, phir wo aasman walon mein manadi kartey hain : be-shak Allah falan shakhs se mohabbat karta hai lihaza tum us se mohabbat karo, aasman waley us se mohabbat kartey hain, phir zamin walon (ke dilon) mein uski maqbooliyat paida kar di jati hai, aur jab Allah Taala kisi bandey se bughz rakhta hai to wo Jibrael (Alaihissalam) ko bula kar farmata hai : be-shak main falan shakhs se bughz rakhta hun lihaza tum bhi us se bughz rakho , Jibrael (Alaihissalam) us se bughz rakhtey hain, phir wo aasman walon mein aelan kartey hain ke Allah falan shakhs se bughz rakhta hai lihaza tum bhi us se bughz rakho , farmaya : wo us se bughz rakhtey hain, phir zamin walon ke dilon mein uskey liye bughz paida kar diya jata hai.'' rawahu Muslim."
5006,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''be-shak Allah roze-qiyamat farmaeyga : meri azmat aur tazeem ki khatir baham (aapas mein) mohabbat karney waley kahan hain? main aaj unko apney saye mein jagah dunga, us din merey saye ke siwa koi saya nahin.'' rawahu Muslim."
5007,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain ke eik aadmi kisi dusri basti mein apney kisi (musalman) bhai ki ziyaarat ke liye gaya to Allah ne uskey raastey main eik farishta bitha diya jo uskey intizar mein tha, (jab wo us farishtey ke paas se guzra to) usney kaha : kahan ka irada hai? us aadmi ne kaha : main us basti mein apney eik (musalman) bhai se milney ja raha hun, usney puchha : kya uska tum par koi ehsan hai jis ka tum badla chukaney ja rahey ho? usney kaha : iskey ilawa aur koi wajeh nahin ke main us se Allah ki khatir mohabbat karta hun, us (farishtey) ne kaha : main Allah ki taraf se tumharey paas pegham lekar aaya hun ke jis tarah tum Allah ki khatir us shakhs se mohabbat kartey ho wesay hi Allah tum se mohabbat karta hai.'' rawahu Muslim."
5008,"Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain : eik aadmi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to usney arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! aap us shakhs ke mutalliq kya farmatey hain jo kuchh logon se mohabbat karta hai lekin wo (sohbat ya ilm aur amal ke lihaz sey) un se mila nahin? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aadmi unke sath hoga jis se uski mohabbat hogi.'' muttafaq aleh."
5009,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke eik aadmi ne arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! qiyamat Kab aaeygi? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tujh par afsos hai, tum ne uskey liye kya tayyari ki hai? '' usney arz kiya : meri tayyari sirf yehi hai ke main Allah aur uskey Rasool se mohabbat karta hun, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tu uskey sath hoga jis se to mohabbat rakhta hai.'' Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine musalmanon ko Islam qubul karney ke baad is baat se ziyada kisi aur chiz se khush hotey huey nahin dekha. muttafaq aleh."
5010,"Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''nek ham nasheen aur burey ham nasheen ki misal aisi hai jaisey kastoori wala aur aag ki bhatti dhonkney wala, kastoori wala ya to wo tumhen Atiya dey dega ya tum khud us se kharid logey ya phir tum us se achchhi khushbu pa lo gey. jabkey bhatti dhonkney wala ya to wo tumharey kapdey jala dega ya tum us se gandi bu paaogey.'' muttafaq aleh."
5011,"Hazrat Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''Allah taala farmata hai : un logon ke liye jo meri khatir baham (aapas mein) mohabbat kartey hain, meri khatir baham (aapas mein) mulaqaten kartey hain, aur meri khatir hi eik doosrey par kharch kartey hain, meri mohabbat wajib ho gaee.'' Maalik. aur Tirmizi ki riwayat mein hai, farmaya : ''Allah taala farmata hai : meri jalalat aur azmat ki khatir baham (aapas mein) mohabbat karney walon ke liye Noor ke member hain, un par Anbiya (Alaihissalam) aur shuhda bhi rashk karengey.'' rawahu Malik aur Tirmizi."
5012,"Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ke bandon mein se kuchh aisey log bhi hain jo na to Anbiya hain aur na shuhda, lekin roze-qiyamat Allah ke yahan unke maqam aur martabe par Anbiya (Alaihissalam) aur shuhda bhi rashk karengey.'' Sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamein bataeyn ke wo kon log hain? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''wo log hain jo aapas mein na to kisi rishtey natey ki wajeh se mohabbat kartey hain na kisi maali sharaakat ki bina par balke wo mehaz Allah ke hukm aur qur'aani ittiba mein baham (aapas mein) mohabbat kartey aur len-den kartey hain, Allah ki qism ! unke chehrey chamaktey hongey aur wo Noor (ke membaron) par hongey, aur jab deegar log khof mein mubtala hongey to wo khof-zada nahin hongey aur jab deegar log gham ka shikar hongey to wo gham-zada nahin hongey.'' phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ye aayat tilawat farmaai : ''sun lo ! be-shak Allah ke doston par na koi khof hoga aur na wo ghamgin hongey.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
5013,"Aur unhon (Imam Baghwi) ne isey Abu-Maalik ki sanad se kuchh zawaayed ke sath Masaabeh ke alfaz se Sharahus-sunnah mein riwayat kiya hai, aur isi tarah Shobil-emaan mein bhi hai. (rawahu fi Sharahus-sunnah aur Masaabeh sunnah aur al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan)."
5014,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya : ''Abu-Zar ! eman ka kon sa hissey (halqa) ziyada mazbut aur mohkam hai?'' unhoney arz kiya, Allah aur uskey Rasool behtar jantey hain. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ki khatir eik doosrey se mohabbat aur taawun karna , Allah ki khatir mohabbat karna aur Allah ki khatir bughz rakhna.'' (rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan)."
5015,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab musalman apney (musalman) bhai ki iyaadat karta hai ya us se mulaqat karta hai to Allah Taala farmata hai : teri aakhirat ki zindagi achchhi ho gaee hai, tera chalna achchhaa ho gaya aur tum ne jannat mein jagah bana li hai.'' Tirmizi, aur farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
5016,"Hazrat Miqdam bin Maadikarb (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab aadmi apney (musalman) bhai se mohabbat karey to wo usey bataey ke wo us se mohabbat karta hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood aur Tirmizi."
5017,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, eik aadmi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas se guzra jabkey kuchh log aap ke paas they, un logon mein se kisi ne kaha : main us shakhs se Allah ki khatir mohabbat karta hun, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya tum ne usey bataya hai?'' usney arz kiya, nahin, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''uski taraf jaao aur usey bataao.'' chunanche wo us shakhs ke paas gaya aur usey bataya (ke main tujh se Allah ki khatir mohabbat karta hun) to usney kaha : jis zaat ki khatir tum mujh se mohabbat kartey ho wo zaat tujh se mohabbat karey. raawi bayan kartey hain, phir wo aadmi wapis aaya to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne us se puchha to usney aap ko uskey jawab se aagah kiya, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum uskey sath hi hogey jis se tum mohabbat kartey ho, aur tum ne jo sawab chaha wo tumhen milega.'' Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan. aur Tirmizi ki riwayat mein hai : ''aadmi jis se mohabbat karta hai usi ke sath hoga, aur jo usney kiya uska wo sila paeyga.'' (rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan aur Tirmizi)."
5018,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''tum sirf kisi momin shakhs ki ham nasheenin (dosti) ikhtiyar karo aur tumhara khana sirf muttaqi shakhs hi khaye.'' rawahu Tirmizi, Abu-Dawood aur Darmi."
5019,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aadmi apney dost ke Deen par hota hai, lihaza tum mein se her eik ko chahiye ke wo dekhey ke wo kis se dosti kar raha hai.'' Ahmed, Tirmizi, Abu-Dawud, Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan. aur Imam Tirmizi (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, aur Imam Nauwi (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : iski sanad sahih hain. (rawahu Ahmed, Tirmizi, Abu-Dawood aur al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan)."
5020,"Hazrat Yazid bin Nuama (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab aadmi kisi aadmi se bhai chaara qaaim karey to wo us se uskey naam, uskey walid ke naam aur uskey qabiley ke mutalliq daryaft kar ley, kyonkey ye mohabbat (dosti) ko ziyada milaaney (badhaney) wala hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
5021,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamarey paas tashrif laye to farmaya : ''kya tum jantey ho ke Allah Taala ko kon se aamaal ziyada pasand hain?'' Sahaba mein se kisi ne arz kya : Namaz , Zakat , aur kisi ne arz kiya : jihad hai. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ke nazdik pasandida amal , Allah ki khatir mohabbat karna aur Allah ki khatir bughz rakhna hai.'' Ahmed. aur Abu-Dawood ne aakhiri hissey riwayat kiya hai. rawahu Ahmed aur Abu-Dawood."
5022,"Hazrat Abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs Allah ki raza ki khatir kisi shakhs se mohabbat karta hai to wo apney Rab aur Shan Wale ki takrim (izzat) karta hai.'' rawahu Ahmed."
5023,"Hazrat Asma binte Yazid (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke usney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''kya main tumhen tumharey behtareen logon ke mutalliq na bataaun?'' Sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! zarur bataeyn, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tumharey behtareen log wo hain ke jab un par nazar padey to Allah yad aa jaey.'' rawahu ibne-Maja."
5024,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar do bandey Shan Wale Allah ki khatir aapas mein mohabbat kartey hain, eik mashriq mein hai aur eik maghrib mein , to roze-qiyamat Allah un dono ko ikhatta kar dega aur farmaeyga : ye hai wo jis se tum meri raza ki khatir mohabbat kiya kartey they.'' (rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan)."
5025,"Hazrat Abu-Rizeen (Laqeet bin Aamir bin Sabra (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey farmaya : ''kya main tumhen is Deen ki buniyad ke mutalliq na bataaun jiskey zariey tum Deen aur duniya ki bhalai hasil kar lo? tum ehale zikr ki majaalis ikhtiyar karo, jab khilwat (akele) mein ho to phir jis qadr ho sakey apni zaban par Allah ka zikr jari rakho aur Allah ki khatir mohabbat karo aur Allah ki khatir bughz rakho. Abu-Rizeen ! kya tumhen malum hai? ke aadmi jab apney (musalman) bhai ki ziyaarat ke liye (ghar sey) nikalta hai to sattar hazar farishtey uskey sath chaltey hain aur wo sab uskey liye duayen kartey jatey hain aur wo kehtey hain : hamarey parwardigar ! usney teri raza ki khatir talluq joda hai to usey (apni rehmat aur maghfirat ke sath) jod dey, agar tum apney jism ko un kamon par laga sako to lagaao.'' (rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan)."
5026,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath tha aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jannat mein yaqoot ke sutoon hain, un par zamarrud ke baala khaney hain, unke darwazey khuley hain, wo chamak daar sitarey ki tarah chamaktey hain.'' Sahaba kiram (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! un mein kon log rahengey? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ki khatir aapas mein mohabbat karney waley, Allah ki khatir aapas mein ham nasheenin ikhtiyar karney waley aur Allah ki khatir aapas mein mulaqat karney waley.'' Imam Behaqi ne teeno hadisen Shobil-emaan mein riwayat ki hain. (rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan)."
5027,"Hazrat Abu-Ayub Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kisi aadmi ke liye jayez nahin ke wo apney (musalman) bhai se teen din se zayed talluqaat khatam karey, dono miltey hain to wo us se aeraz (bacha) karta hai aur wo us se aeraz (bacha) karta hai, aur un dono mein se behtar wo hai jo salam mein pehal karta hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
5028,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''bad-gumaani se bacho, kyonkey bad-gumaani sab se bada jhoot hai, tum kisi ke aeb mat talash karo aur na jaasusi karo, qeemat badhaney ke liye boli mat do aur na baham (aapas mein) hasad karo, bughz mat rakho aur na qata' talluqi karo aur Allah ke bando ! bhai-bhai bin jaao.'' eik dusri riwayat mein hai : ''(aur hasad ki bina par) baham (aapas mein) eik doosrey se aagey badhney ki koshish na karo.'' muttafaq aleh."
5029,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''peer aur Jumerat ke roz jannat ke darwazey kholey jatey hain, shirk se bezar her shakhs ko bakhsh diya jata hai, albatta us shakhs ki maghfirat nahin hoti jiski apney bhai ke sath ranjish aur adawat ho, kaha jata hai : un dono ko mohlat do yahan tak ke wo suleh kar lein.'' rawahu Muslim."
5030,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''her Jumey (saat dino mein) logon ke aamaal do martaba peer aur Jumerat ke roz pesh kiye jatey hain, her momin bande ko bakhsh diya jata hai, albatta us bandey ki maghfirat nahin hoti jiski apney bhai ke sath ranjish aur adawat ho, kaha jata hai : un dono ko chhod do yahan tak ke wo (adawat sey) ruju kar lein.'' rawahu Muslim."
5031,"Hazrat Umme Kulsoom bin Aqba bin Abi Muqeet (Raziallahu anhu) bayan karti hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''logon ke darmiyan suleh karaney wala shakhs jhoota nahin, wo (dono sey) khair aur bhalai ki baat karta hai aur (dono ko) khair aur bhalai ki baat pahunchata hai.'' Imam Muslim ne ye izafa naqal kiya hai : Umme-Kulsoom (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha maine unhen yani Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko teen umur (baton) ke ilawa kisi mamley mein jhoot bolney ki ijazat detey huey nahin suna : ladaai (jang) mein, logon ke darmiyan suleh karaney mein aur miyan biwi ki baham (aapas mein) guftgu karney mein.'' muttafaq aleh."
5032,Aur Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hadees : ''shetan mayus ho chuka.'' (baabul-waswasa) mein zikr ki gaee hai. (rawahu Muslim).
5033,"Hazrat Asma binte Yazid (Raziallahu anhu) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''sirf teen mawaqe par jhoot bolnaa jayez hai, aadmi ka apni biwi ko khush karney ke liye jhoot bolnaa , ladaai mein jhoot bolnaa aur logon ke darmiyan suleh karaney ke liye jhoot bolnaa.'' rawahu Ahmed aur Tirmizi."
5034,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kisi musalman ke liye munasib nahin ke wo kisi musalman se teen din se zayed talluq khatam karey, jab wo us se mulaqat karey to teen martaba usey salam karey, her martaba wo usey salam ka jawab na dey to ye (salam karney wala) us (mulaqat tarak karne ) ke gunah se paak ho jata hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
5035,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kisi musalman ke liye jayez nahin ke wo apney (musalman) bhai se teen din se zayed talluq tarak karey, jis shakhs ne teen din se zayed talluq todey rakhe aur wo (isi haalat mein) faut ho gaya to wo jahannam mein jaeyga.'' rawahu Ahmed aur Abu-Dawood."
5036,Hazrat Abu-Kharaash Salma (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''jisney apney bhai se saal bhar mulaqat tarak ki to wo uskey khoon bahaney ke mutraadif hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood.
5037,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kisi momin ke liye jayez nahin ke wo kisi momin se teen din se zayed mulaqat tarak karey, jab teen din guzar jaeyn to usey chahiye ke wo us se mulaqat karey aur usey salam karey, agar usney salam ka jawab dey diya to wo dono ajr mein shareek hain, aur agar wo salam ka jawab na dey to wohi shakhs gunah gaar hoga jabkey salam karney wala mulaqat tarak karne ke khaaney se nikal jaeyga.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
5038,"Hazrat Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya main tumhen rozey , sadqey aur Namaz se behtar darjey waley amal ke mutalliq na bataaun?'' raawi bayan kartey hain, ham ne arz kiya : zarur bataeyn , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''do fariqon , doston , rishte-daaron ke darmiyan suleh karana , jabkey do fariqon ke darmiyan fasad aisi khaslat hai jo (nekiyon ko) zaayel khatm kar deney wali hai.'' Abu-Dawud, Tirmizi, aur Imam Tirmizi (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : ye hadees sahih hai. rawahu Abu-Dawood aur Tirmizi."
5039,"Hazrat Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''sabiqa (pichhli) ummaton ki bimari (ghair mehsus tareeqey sey) tumhari taraf muntaqil ho gaee hai, hasad aur bughz aur adawat aur wo nekiyon ko zaayel khatm karney wali hai, main ye nahin keh raha ke wo (bimari) baal moond'ti hai balke wo Deen ko khatam kar deti hai.'' rawahu Ahmed aur Tirmizi."
5040,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''hasad se bacho kyonkey hasad nekiyon ko is tarah kha jata hai jis tarah aag lakdi ko kha jati hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
5041,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwaayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''do (fariqon , doston , rishte-daaron) ke darmiyan burai dalney se bacho kyonkey wo (deen ko) zaayel khatm karney wali hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
5042,"Hazrat Abu-Sirma (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs kisi (musalman) ko takleef pahunchata hai to uskey badley mein Allah usey takleef pahunchata hai, aur jo shakhs kisi ko mashaqqat mein mubtala karta hai to Allah usey mashaqqat mein mubtala kar deta hai.'' ibne-Maja , Tirmizi, aur unhoney farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu ibne-Maja aur Tirmizi."
5043,"Hazrat Abu-Bakar Siddiq (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''wo shakhs mala'oon hai jo kisi momin ko nuqsan pahunchata hai ya usey dhoka deta hai.'' Tirmizi, aur unhoney farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
5044,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) member par chadhey aur ba-aawaze-buland farmaya : ''aey logo ! jo apni zaban se Islam laye ho jabkey eman unke dilon tak nahin pahuncha , tum musalmanon ko takleef mat pahunchaao aur na unhen sharm dilaao aur na hi unki kamiyan talash karo, kyonkey jo shakhs apney (musalman) bhai ki kamiyan talash karta hai to Allah uskey aibon ka peechha karta hai, aur jiskiy kamiyon ka Allah peechha karta hai to wo usey ruswa kar deta hai chahey wo apney ghar ke wast (beech) mein ho.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
5045,"Hazrat Saeed bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''sood ki sab se sangeen surat musalman ki izzat ke barey mein zaban darazi karna hai.'' (rawahu Abu-Dawood aur al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan)."
5046,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab merey rab ne mujhey Mairaj karaai to main aisey logon ke paas se guzra jinkey nakhun tanbey ke they, wo apney chehron aur seenon ko noch rahey they, maine kaha : Jibrael ! ye kon log hain? unhoney kaha : ye wo log hain jo logon ka gosht khaya kartey they (unki gheebat kiya kartey they) aur unki izzaton ke mutalliq aeb-juee kartey they.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
5047,"Hazrat Mustaurid (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jisney kisi musalman aadmi (ki gheebat) ki wajeh se eik luqma khaya to Allah us shakhs ko uski jaisi jahannam se khilaaeyga aur jis shakhs ne kisi musalman aadmi ki (gheebat ki) ki wajeh se koi kapda pehna to Allah us shakhs ko uski jaisi jahannam se (kapda) pahnaaeyga aur jo shakhs shohrat aur riyaakaari ki jagah khada hua to Allah usko roze-qiyamat shohrat aur riyaakaarii ki jagah par khada kerega.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
5048,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Husne guman, Husne ibadat mein se hai.'' rawahu Ahmed aur Abu-Dawood."
5049,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Safiya (Raziallahu anhu) ka oont bimar ho gaya jabkey Zenab (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas zayed sawari thi, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Zenab (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya : ''us (Safiya (Raziallahu anhu)) ko oont dey do.'' unhoney kaha : main us yahoodan ko dun ! Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) naraz huey aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne zul-hijja, muhrram aur safar ke chand dinon tak un se sohbat tarak kar di. rawahu Abu-Dawood. aur Muaz bin Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hadees : ''jo shakhs kisi momin ki izzat bachata hai.'' (باب الشفقۃ و الرحمۃ) mein guzar chuki hai."
5050,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Esa bin Maryam (Alaihissalam) ne eik aadmi ko chori kartey huey dekha to Esa (Alaihissalam) ne usey farmaya : tum ne chori ki hai, usney kaha, us zaat ki qism jiskey siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin ! hergiz nahin, (us par) Esa (Alaihissalam) ne farmaya : main Allah par eman laya , aur maine apney nafs ka inkaar kiya.'' rawahu Muslim."
5051,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''qarib hai ke faqr (Allah par aetraz karney ki wajeh sey) kufr bin jaey aur qarib hai ke hasad taqdir par ghalib aa jaey.'' (rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan)."
5052,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs apney (musalman) bhai ke samney uzr pesh karey aur wo usey mazoor na samjhey ya wo uska uzr qubul na karey to is par tex wasul karney waley ke jaisa gunah hota hai.'' (rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan). ye dono riwaayatein Imam Behaqi ne Shobil-emaan mein riwayat ki hain, aur farmaya : (المکاس) se ushr (daswan hissa) leney wala murad hai."
5053,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''momin eik surakh se do martaba nahin dasaa jata.'' muttafaq aleh."
5054,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Abd Qais ke sardar Ashajj se farmaya : ''tum mein do khaslatein aisi hain jinhen Allah pasand farmata hai : hilm (burdbari) aur waqar.'' rawahu Muslim.
5055,"Hazrat Sehal bin Saad Saaidi (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''burdbaari Allah ki janib se hai aur jald bazi shetan ki janib se hai.'' Imam Tirmizi ne is hadees ko riwayat kiya hai, aur isey gharib kaha hai aur baaz muhaddeseen ne is hadees ke raawi Abdul Muhemin bin Abbas ke haafze ke mutalliq kalam kiya hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
5056,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''laghzish karney wala hi burdbar (samajhdar) hota hai aur tajarbe-kaar hi daanaa (aqalmand) hota hai.'' Ahmed, Tirmizi, aur Imam Tirmizi (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. rawahu Ahmed aur Tirmizi."
5057,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke eik aadmi ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se arz kiya : aap mujhey wasiyat farmaeyn, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''maamley par ghor aur fikr kar , agar to uskey anjam mein khair aur bhalai dekhey to usey kar guzar aur agar tujhey gumrahi ka andesha lagey to usey mat kar.''  (jazaa munkir) rawahu fi Sharahus-sunnah)."
5058,"Hazrat Musab bin Saad (Raziallahu anhu) apney walid se riwayat kartey hain, jabkey Aamash ne farmaya : main to is (hadees) ko Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hi se janta hun, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''amale-aakhirat ke ilawa her chiz mein ujlat (jaldi) se kaam na lena behtar hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
5059,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Sarjis (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''achchhi seerat , tahammul aur waqar aur beech ki raah ikhtiyar karna nabuwat ka chaubeeswaan hissey hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
5060,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''achchhaa tariqa aur achchhi seerat nabuwat ka pachcheeswaan hissey hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood.
5061,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab aadmi baat kartey huey idhar-udhar dekhey (ke kahin koi aur to nahin sun raha) to wo amanat hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi aur Abu-Dawood."
5062,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne abu-Haisam bin tahiyan se farmaya : ''kya tumharey paas koi khaadim hai.'' usney arz kya : nahin, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab hamarey paas qaidi ayen to phir tum hamarey paas aana .'' Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas do ghulam laye gaey to abu-Haisam bhi aap ke paas gaey . Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' un mein se koi eik pasand kar lo .''unhoney arz kya, Allah ke nabi! aap hi pasand farma den, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs se mashwara talab kya jaey to wo ameen hota hai, usey ley lo kyonkey maine usey Namaz padhtey huey dekha hai, main tumhen uskey sath achcha suluk karney ki wasiyat karta hun.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
5063,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''teen majaalis, ( jahan ( nahaq qatl karney ya zina karney ya nahaq maal hasil karney ke mutalliq baaten ho rahi hun, ke ilawa majaalis (ki baaten) amanat hoti hain.'' ( rawahu Abu-Dawood) . aur abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hadees ke : ''be-shak badi amanat '' (baabul-mubashra) ki fasal awwal mein zikr ho chuki hai."
5064,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab Allah ne aql ko paida farmaya to usey farmaya : khadi ho ja, wo khadi ho gaee, phir usey kaha : peechey mud, to wo peechey mud gaee, phir usey kaha : samney tawajjoh kar, to wo samney aa gaee, phir usey kaha : beth ja, to wo beth gaee, phir usey farmaya : maine apni puri makhluq mein tujhey sab se ziyada behtar w afzal aur sab se achcha banaya hai, main teri wajeh se muwakhiza karunga, teri wajeh se inayat karunga aur teri wajeh se main pehchaana jata hun, main teri wajeh se saza dunga jaza aur sawab ka inhisaar bhi tujh par hai.'' uskey mutalliq baaz ulamaa ne kalam kya hai. (rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan) ."
5065,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''bala shubha eik shakhs Namaz padhney walon, roza rakhney walon, Zakat deney walon, Haj aur Umra karney walon mein hoga.'' yahan tak ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne tamam achey kamon ka zikr kya. ''lekin us shakhs ko sawab uski aql ke tanaasub se diya jaeyga.'' (rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan) ."
5066,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey farmaya : '' abu-Zar! tadbeer jaisi koi aql nahin aur mushtbihaat se ruk janey jaisa koi taqwa nahin aur na hi Hasne-khulq jaisa koi hasb w sharf hai.'' (rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan)."
5067,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kharch karney mein miyaana rawi nisf maeeshat hai, ( achey ( logon se dosti aur mohabbat nisf aql hai, aur Husne-sawal nisf ilm hai.'' Imam Behaqi ne ye chaaron ahadis Shobil-emaan mein naqal ki hain. munkir, ( rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( ."
5068,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''be-shak Allah Taala narmi karney wala hai, narmi ko pasand farmata hai, aur wo jis qadr narmi par ata karta hai, wo sakhti par ata nahin karta na uskey ilawa kisi aur chiz par ata karta hai.'' aur Muslim hi ki riwayat mein hai : aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se farmaya : ''narmi ikhtiyar karo, sakhti aur bad-zabaani se bacho, be-shak jis chiz mein narmi hoti hai to wo us ( chiz ( ko muzayyan kar deti hai aur jis chiz se usey nikal liya jata hai to wo usey aeb daar bana deti hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
5069,"Hazrat Jarir (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''narmi se mehroom shakhs (her qism ki) khair w bhalai se mehroom hai.'' rawahu Muslim."
5070,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ansaar ke eik aadmi ke paas se guzrey jo apney bhai ko haya ke mutalliq nasihat kar raha tha (ke itney sharmeeley na bano) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''usey chhod do, kyonkey haya eman ka hissa hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
5071,"Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''haya khair hi lata hai.'' eik riwayat mein hai : ''haya to saraapaa khair hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
5072,"Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''logon ne sabiqa Anbiya (Alaihissalam) ke kalam se jo paya hai is mein ye (maqoola) bhi hai ke jab to haya nahin karta to phir jo chahey so kar.'' Bukhari ."
5073,"Hazrat Nawaas bin Samaan (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se neki aur gunah ke mutalliq puchha to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''neki, achcha akhlaq hai, jabkey gunah wo hai jo terey dil mein khatkey aur to napasand karey ke log us se muttla ho jaeyn.'' rawahu Muslim ."
5074,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum mein se mujhey sab se ziyada mehbub shakhs wo hai jo tum mein akhlaq mein sab se ziyada achcha hai.'' Bukhari ."
5075,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum mein sab se behtar shakhs wo hai jo tum mein akhlaq mein sab se ziyada achcha hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
5076,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ko narmi se uska hissey diya gaya to usey duniya w aakhirat ki bhalai se uska hissey diya gaya aur jo shakhs narmi se apney hissey se mehroom kar diya gaya to wo duniya w aakhirat mein apney hissey ki bhalai se mehroom kar diya gaya .'' ( rawahu fi Sharahus-sunnah ( ."
5077,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''haya eman ka hissa hai, aur eman ( waley ( jannat mein hongey, jabkey fohsh goi burai hai aur burai (waley) jahannam mein jaeyngey.'' rawahu Ahmed w Tirmizi."
5078,"Hazrat Muzena qabiley ke aadmi se riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya : Allah ke Rasool! insan ko jo ata kya gaya hai is mein sab se behtar chiz konsi hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Husne-khulq.'' ( rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan)."
5079,aur Sharahus-sunnah mein Usama bin shareek se marwi (bayan) hai. (rawahu fi Sharahus-sunnah) .
5080,"Hazrat Harisa bin Wahab (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''bad akhlaq aur sakht dil insan jannat mein dakhil nahin hoga.'' Abu-Dawud, Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan. aur Jaame ul-usool waley ne bhi usey riwayat kya hai, aur is mein Harisa se marwi (bayan) hai, aur isi tarah unhi se Sharahus-sunnah mein bhi marwi (bayan) hai, aur uskey alfaz ye hain, farmaya : '' ( جواظ w جعظری ( '' jannat mein nahin jaeyga.'' جعظری ka ye maana kaha jata hai : '' sakht khoo aur sakht bhale hi .'' aur masaabeh ke nuskhon mein Ikrima bin Wahab se marwi (bayan) hai, aur uskey alfaz hain : ''( جواظ )'' ka maana hai : maal jama karney wala bakheel, aur '' ( جعظری ( '' ka maana hai : '' sakht khoo aur sakht go.'' ( rawahu Abu-Dawood w al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan w fi Sharahus-sunnah w zikr fi المصابیح السنہ ( ."
5081,"Hazrat abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu), Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''roze-qiyamat momin ki meezaan mein Hasan khalq se ziyada bhari chiz koi nahin rakhi jaeygi, aur Allah yaqinan bad-zaban aur be-hooda baaten karney waley ko pasand nahin farmata.'' Tirmizi, aur farmaya : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, aur Abu-Dawood ne pehla hissey riwayat kya hai. rawahu Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood ."
5082,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''be-shak momin apney husne-khulq ki wajeh se rozey daar aur tahajjud guzar shakhs ka darja pa leta hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
5083,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey farmaya : ''tum jahan bhi ho Allah se dartey raho, aur burai ke baad neki karo wo us (burai) ko mita degi, aur logon ke sath Hasan akhlaq ke sath pesh aao.'' rawahu Ahmad Tirmizi w Darmi ."
5084,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya main tumhen aisey logon ke mutalliq na bataaun jo jahannam ki aag par ya jahannam ki aag un par haram hai? wo her aasani karney waley, narmi karney waley, qarib rehney waley, naram khoo par haram hai.'' Ahmed, Tirmizi, aur farmaya : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. rawahu Ahmed w Tirmizi ."
5085,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' momin bhola-bhala sakhi hota hai jabkey faajir dhoka baaz, bakheel hota hai.'' rawahu Ahmed w Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood."
5086,"Hazrat Mak-hool bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''momin narm mizaj aur ba-waqar hotey hain jaisey mahaar daar oont, jab usey chalaya jata hai to chal padta hai aur agar usey chattan par bithaya jata hai to wo beth jata hai.'' Imam Tirmizi ne usey mursal riwayat kya hai. rawahu Tirmizi ."
5087,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' aisa musalman jo logon ke sath mil jul kar rehta hai aur unki takleefon par sabr karta hai wo us se afzal hai jo unke sath mil jal kar nahin rehta aur na unki takleefon par sabr karta hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi w ibne-Maja."
5088,"Hazrat Sehal bin Muaz apney walid se riwayat kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs ghussey par qabu paata hai jabkey wo us (ghussey) ko nikal sakta hai to Allah roze-qiyamat usey sari makhluq ke samney layega aur usey apni pasand ki Hoor ikhtiyar karney ka ikhtiyar dega .'' Tirmizi, Abu-Dawood . aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood ."
5089,"aur Abu-Dawood ki riwayat mein hai ke, Suwed bin Wahab ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke as-haab ki aulad mein se kisi aadmi se riwayat kya, usney apney walid sey, farmaya : ''Allah uskey dil ko aman w eman ke sath bhar dega.'' aur Suwed se marwi (bayan) hadees : ''jisney khoobsurat libas pehanna tarak kar diya.'' kitabul-libas mein zikr ki gaee hai. rawahu Abu-Dawood."
5090,"Hazrat Zaid bin Talha (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''be-shak her Deen ki kuch khas khususiyat hain aur Islam ki khas khususiyat haya hai.'' Imam Malik ne usey mursal riwayat kya hai. rawahu Malik."
5091,Hazrat ibne-Maja ne aur Behaqi ne Shobil-emaan mein Anas aur ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kya hai. ( rawahu ibne-Maja w al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( .
5092,Hazrat ibne-Maja ne aur Behaqi ne Shobil-emaan mein Anas aur ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kya hai. ( rawahu ibne-Maja w al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( .
5093,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' be-shak haya aur eman sath sath hain, jab un dono mein se eik utha liya jata hai to doosra bhi utha liya jata hai.'' ( rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( ."
5094,"aur ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ki riwayat mein hai, farmaya : ''jab in mein se eik ko salb kar liya jata hai to doosra bhi uskey peechey chala jata hai.'' ( rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( ."
5095,"Hazrat Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab maine rikaab mein paaon rakha to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne aakhiri wasiyat kartey huey mujhey farmaya : ''Muaz! logon ke sath achey akhlaq se pesh aana.'' rawahu Malik."
5096,"Hazrat Imam Malik (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, mujhey ye baat pahunchi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''mujhey achey akhlaq ki takmil ke liye maboos kya gaya hai.'' rawahu Malik."
5097,Hazrat Imam Ahmed ne Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kya hai. rawahu Ahmed .
5098,"Hazrat Jaafar bin Muhammad apney walid se riwayat kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab aaina dekhtey to ye dua padhtey : ''her qism ki tareef Allah ke liye hai jisney meri surat w seerat ko behtar banaya aur merey ilawa kisi mein jo aeb tha mujhey us se mehfooz karkey muzayyan banaya.'' Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan, mursal riwayat hai, (rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan) ."
5099,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) dua kya kartey they : ''aey Allah ! to ne mujhey achi tarah takhleeq farmaya, pas merey akhlaq bhi sanwaar dey .'' rawahu Ahmed ."
5100,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya main tum mein sab se behtar logon ke barey mein na bataaun ?'' unhoney arz kya, zarur bataeyn , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum mein se sab se behtar log wo hain jinki tum mein se umrein lambi hon aur wo tum mein se behtareen akhlaq ke hamil hon.'' rawahu Ahmed ."
5101,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''sab se kamil eman waley wo log hain jo un mein sabse behtar akhlaq waley hain.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood w Darmi ."
5102,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke kisi aadmi ne abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ko gaali di, jabkey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tashrif farma they, aap tajjub kar rahey they aur muskura rahey they, jab usney ziyada badtameezi ki to abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne uski kisi baat ka jawab diya is par Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) naraz ho kar uth khadey huey. abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) aap ke paas gaey aur arz kya : Allah ke Rasool! wo mujhey gaaliyaan diye ja raha tha jabkey aap tashrif farma they, jab maine uski kisi baat ka jawab diya to aap naraz ho kar uth khadey huey . aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' tumharey sath farishta tha jo usey jawab dey raha tha, aur jab tum ne usey jawab diya to shetan waqey ho gaya .'' phir farmaya : '' abu-Bakar ! teen chizen mukammal taur par haq hain, jis shakhs ki haq talfi ki jaey aur wo Allah azz-w-jall ki khatir us se chashm poshi karta hai to uskey badley mein Allah usey quwat w nusrat ata farmata hai, jo shakhs sila rehmi ki khatir Atiya deta hai to Allah uskey badley mein usey ziyada ata farmata hai aur jo shakhs kasrat ( maal ( ki khatir daste-sawal daraz karta hai to Allah mazeed qillat farma deta hai.'' rawahu Ahmed."
5103,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah jis ghar walon ke sath narmi ka irada farmata hai to wo unhen nafa pahunchata hai, aur jis ghar walon ko us se mehroom kar deta hai to wo unhen uski wajeh se nuqsan pahuncha deta hai.'' ( rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( ."
5104,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke eik aadmi ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se darkhast ki, mujhey wasiyat farmaeyn, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ghussa na kya kar.'' usney kaee baar yehi darkhast ki, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ( her baar yehi ( farmaya : ''ghussa na kya kar .'' Bukhari."
5105,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kisi ko pachhadney wala shakhs ziyada taqatwar nahin, taqatwar shakhs to wo hai jo ghussey ke waqt apney aap par qabu rakhey.'' muttafaq aleh."
5106,"Hazrat Harisa bin Wahab (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya main tumhen jannatiyon ke barey mein na bataaun? her zaeef shakhs, ke log usey zaeef w naatawaan samjhen agar wo Allah par qism utha ley to wo usey pura farma dey. kya main tumhen jahannamiyon ke barey mein na bataaun? her sarkash, bakheel aur mutakabbir.'' aur Muslim ki riwayat mein hai : ''her bakheel, kamina aur mutakabbir shakhs.'' muttafaq aleh."
5107,"Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ke dil mein raai ke daney ke barabar eman hoga wo jahannam mein nahin jaeyga aur jis shakhs ke dil mein raai ke daney ke barabar takabbur hoga wo jannat mein nahin jaeyga.'' rawahu Muslim ."
5108,"Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ke dil mein raai ke daney ke barabar takabbur hoga wo jannat mein nahin jaeyga.'' eik aadmi ne arz kya, aadmi pasand karta hai ke uska libas aur uskey jootey achey hon. ( kya ye bhi takabbur hai? (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''be-shak Allah sahibe-jamaal hai aur wo jamaal ko pasand farmata hai, takabbur se murad, haq baat ko thukrana aur logon ko haqeer janna hai.'' rawahu Muslim ."
5109,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' teen aadmi aisey hain, jin se Allah roze-qiyamat kalam nahin farmaeyga aur na unhen paak kerega.'' eik riwayat mein hai. aur na hi unki taraf nazar rehmat se dekhega aur unke liye dardnak azab hoga : boodha zaani, jhoota badshah aur mutakabbir faqir.'' rawahu Muslim ."
5110,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah taala farmata hai : badai meri chadar hai aur azmat mera izaar hai, jo shakhs un dono mein se kisi eik ko kheenchega mein usey aag mein dakhil karunga.'' eik dusri riwayat mein hai : ''main usey aag mein phenkunga.'' rawahu Muslim ."
5111,"Hazrat Salma bin Akwa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aadmi apney aap ko bada samajhta rehta hai yahan tak ke wo sarkashon zalimon ki catagory mein likha jata hai, chunanche jis (azab) mein wo mubtala huey ye bhi usi mein mubtala hoga.'' rawahu Tirmizi ."
5112,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib apney walid se aur wo apney dada se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kiya, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''takabbur karney walon ko roze-qiyamat aadmiyon ki surat mein cheentiyon ke jaise jama kiya jaeyga, her jagah se zillat unhen dhanp leygi , unhen jahannam mein bolas naami jail ki taraf haanka jaeyga aagon ki aag (sab se badi aag) unhen gher legi aur unhen jahannamiyon ki tintul-khabaal naami peep pilai jaeygi.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
5113,"Hazrat Atiya bin Urwa Sa'dii bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ghussa shetan ki taraf se hai, jabkey shetan aag se paida kiya gaya hai, aur aag pani hi se bujhaai jati hai, jab tum mein se kisi ko ghussa aaye to wo wuzu karey.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
5114,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se kisi ko ghussa aaye aur wo khada ho to beth jaey, agar ghussa khatam ho jaey to theek warna let jaey.'' rawahu Ahmed aur Tirmizi."
5115,"Hazrat Asma binte-Umais (Raziallahu anhu) bayan karti hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''bura hai wo banda jisney takabbur kiya aur us badi buland zaat (Allah taalaa) ko bhool gaya, bura hai wo banda jisney zulm aur ziyadti ki aur wo ghalib aur aa'laa zaat ko bhool gaya, bura hai wo banda jo bhool gaya, khel-kood mein mashghool raha aur wo qabron aur apney boseedah honey ko bhool gaya, bura hai wo banda jisney takabbur kiya aur sarkashi ki aur wo (apney) aaghaz aur anjam ko bhool gaya, bura hai wo banda jo Deen ke badley duniya talab karta hai, bura hai wo banda jo shub'haat ke zariey Deen ko kharab karta hai, bad-tareen wo banda hai jisey tamaa (lalach) aur hirs khinch ley jati hai, bura hai wo banda ke khahish usey gumrah kar deti hai, bura hai wo banda jisey duniya ki raghbat zaleel kar deti hai.'' Tirmizi, Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan , dono ne farmaya : iski sanad qawi nahin, aur Imam Tirmizi ne ye bhi farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. (rawahu Tirmizi aur al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan)."
5116,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' wo banda jo Allah Taala ki raza ki khatir ghussay ka ghoont pi jata hai wo ghoont Shan Wale Allah ke nazdik sab se behtar hai.'' rawahu Ahmed."
5117,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne Allah Taala ke us farman (اِدْفَعْ بِالَّتِیْ ھِیَ اَحْسَنُ) ki tafseer kartey huey farmaya : ghussay ke waqt sabr karna, ghalati sarzad ho janey par darguzar karna , jab wo aisey karengey to Allah unhen bachaeyga aur unke dushman sarningun ho jaeyngey goya wo qaribi jigri dost hai.'' Imam Bukhari ne isey muallaq riwayat kiya hai. (Bukhari fi tafseer  baab 4- qabl padhi. 4816 تعلیقا بدون sanad ( ."
5118,"Hazrat Behaz bin Hakim apney walid se aur wo apney dada se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ghussa eman ko is tarah kharab kar deta hai jis tarah ailwa shehad ko kharab kar deta hai.'' (rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan)."
5119,"Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhoney member par farmaya : logo ! tawaazeh (mehman nawaazi) ikhtiyar karo, kyonkey maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''jo shakhs Allah ki khatir tawaazeh ikhtiyar karta hai to Allah usey rifat ata karta hai, wo khud ko apni nazron main to chhota khayal karta hai jabkey logon ki nazron mein azeem hota hai, aur jo shakhs takabbur karta hai, Allah usey pasti ka shikar kar deta hai, wo logon ki nigahon mein chhota hota hai jabkey wo apney aap ko bada tasawwur karta hai, yahan tak ke wo unke nazdik kuttey ya khinzir se bhi zaleel aur haqeer hota hai.'' (rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan)."
5120,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Musa bin Imran (Alaihissalam) ne arz kiya : rab ji ! terey bandon mein se kon sa shakhs terey nazdik ziyada moazziz hai? farmaya : wo shakhs jo qudrat honey ke bawajud maaf kar dey.'' (rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan)."
5121,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs apni zaban ki hifazat karta hai, Allah uskey kamiyon par parda dal deta hai, jo shakhs apney ghussay ko rok leta hai, roze-qiyamat Allah us se apna azab rok lega aur jo shakhs Allah ke huzur mazrat (maafi) karta hai, Allah uski mazrat qubul farma leta hai.'' (rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan)."
5122,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''teen chizen baaise-najat hain aur teen chizen baaise-halakat hain baaise-najat chizen ye hain : zahir aur baatin mein Allah ka taqwa ikhtiyar karna , raza aur narazi mein haq baat karna , aur tawangari aur mohtaji mein darmiyani raah ikhtiyar karna , aur baaise halakat chizen ye hain : aisi khahish jiski ittiba ki jaey, aisa bukhl jiski itaat ki jaey, aur insan ki khud-pasandi, aur ye un sab se ziyada mohlik hai.'' Imam Behaqi ne paanchon hadise Shobil-emaan mein naqal ki hain. (rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan)."
5123,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''zulm roze-qiyamat kaee andheron ka baais hoga.'' muttafaq aleh.
5124,"Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' be-shak Allah zalim ko dheel deta rehta hai lekin wo jab usey pakadta hai to phir usey chhodta nahin.'' phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ye aayat tilawat farmaai : ''terey rab ki pakad isi tarah hoti hai jab wo basti ke zalimon ko pakadta hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
5125,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab maqame Hajar ke paas se guzrey to farmaya : ''tum un masaakino (bastiyon) mein, jahan ke bashindon ne apney ooper zulm kiya, rotey huey dakhil hona kyonkey jis azab mein wo mubtala huey kahin tum bhi is mein mubtala na ho jaao.'' phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apna sar dhanp liya aur raftaar tez kar di yahan tak ke wo wadi se guzar gaey. muttafaq aleh."
5126,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs par apney (musalman) bhai ka, uski izzat se mutalliq ya kisi aur chiz se mutalliq koi haq ho to wo (duniya mein), us se maafi talaafi karwa ley iskey pahle ke wo din aa jaey jab uskey paas dirham aur Dinar nahin hongey, agar uskey paas amal Saleh hongey to wo us se uskey zulm ke ba-qadr ley liye jaeyngey, aur agar uski nekiyan nahin hongi to haq-daar ke gunah lekar is par dal diye jaeyngey.'' Bukhari."
5127,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya tum jantey ho muflis kon hai? ''unhoney arz kiya, jis shakhs ke paas dirham hon na maal aur mataa (daulat) , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''meri ummat mein se muflis wo shakhs hai jo roze-qiyamat Namaz , rozey aur Zakat lekar aaeyga aur wo bhi aa jaeyga jisey usney gaali di hogi , jis kisi par bohtan lagaya hoga, jis kisi ka maal khaya hoga, jis kisi ka khoon bahaayaa hoga aur jis kisi ko maara peetaa hoga, us (mazloom) ko uski nekiyon mein se nekiyan de-di jaeyngi, aur agar uskey zimmey huquq ki adaegi se pehley hi uski nekiyan khatam ho gaeen to un (haq-daaron) ke gunah lekar us shakhs par dal diye jaeyngey phir usey jahannam mein phenk diya jaeyga.'' rawahu Muslim."
5128,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum roze-qiyamat haq daaron ko unke huquq zarur ada karogey, yahan tak ke seengon wali bakri se seengon ke baghair bakri ko badla dilaaya jaeyga.'' rawahu Muslim. aur Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hadees : ''zulm se bacho.'' (baabul-infaaq) mein zikr ki gaee hai."
5129,"Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Immaa na banuo, (wo is tarah ke) tum kaho : agar logon ne achchha suluk kiya to ham bhi achchha suluk karengey, aur agar unhoney zulm kiya to ham bhi zulm karengey, balke tum apney aap se azm karo ke agar logon ne achchha suluk kiya to tum bhi achchha suluk karogey aur agar unhoney bura sulook kiya to tum zulm nahin karogey.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
5130,"Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhoney Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke naam khat likha ke aap ikhtisaar ke sath mujhey wasiyat likhen , chunanche unhoney likha : salam tum par ! maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''jo shakhs logon ki narazi ke badley mein Allah ki raza talash karta hai to Allah usey logon ke shar se kafi ho jata hai, aur jo shakhs Allah ki narazi ke badley mein logon ki khushi talash karta hai to Allah usey logon ke supurd kar deta hai.''salamti ho tum par ! rawahu Tirmizi."
5131,"Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab ye aayat nazil hui : ''jo log eman laye aur unhoney apney eman ke sath zulm ki aamezish (milawet) nahin ki.'' ye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke Sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) par giraan guzri aur unhoney arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! ham mein se kon hai jisney apney aap par zulm nahin kiya, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''us se ye murad nahin, balke us se murad shirk hai, kya tum ne Luqman (Alaihissalam) ka qol nahin suna jo unhoney apney bete se kaha : ''bete ! Allah ke sath shirk na karna, kyonkey shirk zulme-azeem hai.'' eik dusri riwayat mein hai : ''aisey nahin jo tum guman kartey ho, ye to wo hai jaisey Luqman (Alaihissalam) ne apney bete se farmaya tha.'' muttafaq aleh."
5132,Hazrat Abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''roze-qiyamat maqam aur martabey ke lihaz se wo shakhs bad-tareen hoga jisney kisi ki duniya (bananey) ki khatir apni aakhirat zaya kar li.'' rawahu ibne-Maja.
5133,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aamaal namey teen qism ke hain, eik wo aamaal nama jisey Allah maaf nahin farmaeyga , wo Allah ke sath shareek karna hai, Allah farmata hai : ''be-shak Allah maaf nahin karta ke uskey sath shirk kiya jaey.'' eik wo aamaal nama hai jisey Allah nahin chhodeyga , wo hai bandon ka aapas mein zulm karna yahan tak ke wo eik doosrey se badla ley lein , aur eik wo namae-aamaal hai jiski Allah parwah nahin kerega, wo hai bandon ka apney aur Allah ke darmiyan zulm karna, ye Allah ke supurd hai, agar wo chahey to usey azab dey dey aur agar chahey to us se darguzar farmaey.'' (rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan)."
5134,"Hazrat Ali bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''mazloom ki badduaa se bacho, wo Allah Taala se apney haq ka mutalba karta hai aur be-shak Allah haq daar se uska haq nahin rokta.'' (rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan)."
5135,"Hazrat Aus bin Shurehbil (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''jo shakhs zalim ke sath chalta hai ta ke wo usko taqwiyat pahunchaey halanke wo janta hai ke wo zalim hai, aisa shakhs Islam se khaarij ho jata hai.'' (rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan)."
5136,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhoney eik aadmi ko bayan kartey huey suna ke zalim shakhs apney aap hi ko nuqsan pahunchata hai, Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : haan, Allah ki qism ! yahan tak ke surkhaab zalim ke zulm ki wajeh se dubli patli ho kar apney aashyaane hi mein mar jati hai. Imam Behaqi ne chaaron hadise Shobil-emaan mein riwayat ki hain. (rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan)."
5137,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum mein se jo shakhs burai dekhey to wo usey apney haath se badal dey , agar wo taqat na rakhey to phir apni zaban sey, agar wo (is ki bhi) istataat na rakhey to phir apney dil se (badalney ke liye mansuba bandi karey aur us se nafrat rakhey), aur ye eman ka kamzor tareen darja hai.'' rawahu Muslim."
5138,"Hazrat Noman bin Bashir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ki hudood (qaaim kerney) mein susti karney waley aur un mein mubtala honey waley shakhs ki misal us qom ki jaisi hai jinhonne eik kashti (mein sawar honey) ke mutalliq qura andazi ki to un mein se baaz uski nichli manzil par aur baaz baalai (upri) manzil par beth gaey, jo nichli manzil mein they wo pani leney ke liye baalai (upri) manzil walon ke ooper se guzartey , jis se ooper waley takleef mehsus kartey , lihaza nichli manzil walon ne kulhaada pakda aur kashti ke nichley hissey mein surakh karney lagey , chunanche ooper waley unke paas aaye aur puchha : tumhen kya hua? unhoney jawab diya ke (hamarey ooper janey sey) tumhen takleef hoti hai aur pani bhi hamari majburi hai, agar ooper walon ne uskey haath rok liye to wo usey bhi bacha lengey aur apney aap ko bhi bacha lengey , aur agar usey (uskey haal par) chhod dengey to wo usey bhi halak kar dengey aur apney aap ko bhi halak kar lengey.'' Bukhari."
5139,"Hazrat Usama bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''roze-qiyamat eik aadmi laya jaeyga aur usey jahannam mein dal diya jaeyga, uski antadiyaan aag mein nikal ayengi , wo unke gird is tarah chakkar lagaeyga jis tarah gadhaa chakki ke gird chakkar lagata hai, jahannami is par jama ho jaeyngey, aur us se daryaft karengey : aey falan ! tumhen kya hua? kya to hamein neki karney ka hukm nahin deta tha aur hamein burai karney se nahin rokta tha? wo kahega : main tumhen neki ka hukm deta tha lekin khud neki nahin karta tha, aur main tumhen burai se rokta tha aur khud uska irtikab (kiya) karta tha.'' muttafaq aleh."
5140,"Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''us zaat ki qism jiskey haath mein meri jaan hai ! tum zarur neki ka hukm karo aur burai se mana karo, warna qarib hai ke Allah tum par apna azab nazil kar dey , phir tum us se duayen karogey lekin wo qubul na hongi.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
5141,"Hazrat Urs bin Umaira (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab zamin par gunah kiya jaey aur wahan mojud shakhs usey napasand karey to wo us shakhs ki manind hai jo wahan mojud nahin, aur jo shakhs us waqt wahan mojud na ho lekin wo is par razi ho to wo us shakhs ki manind hai jo wahan mojud ho.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
5142,"Hazrat Abu-Bakar Siddiq (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai unhoney farmaya : ''logo ! tum ye aayat tilawat kartey ho : ''emaan walo ! tum (gunahon ke mutalliq) apna khayal rakho , jab tum hidayat par ho to phir gumrah shakhs tumhen nuqsan nahin pahuncha sakta. ''maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''be-shak jab log kisi burai ko dekhengey aur usey roken gey nahin to phir qarib hai ke Allah un sab ko apney azab ki lapet mein le-ley.'' ibne-Maja , Tirmizi, aur Imam Tirmizi ne isey sahih qarar diya hai. aur Abu-Dawood ki riwayat mein hai : ''jab wo zalim ko (zulm kartey huey) dekhen aur wo uskey haathon ko na roken to phir qarib hai ke Allah un sab ko azab ki lapet mein le-ley.'' aur Abu-Dawood ki dusri riwayat mein hai : ''jis qom mein gunah hotey hon phir wo unhen rokney ki taqat ke bawajud na roken to qarib hai ke Allah unhen azab ki lapet mein le-ley.'' eik aur riwayat mein hai : ''jis qom ki aqaliyat gunah mein mubtala ho jaey aur wo aksariyat jo gunah to nahin karti magar karney walon ko rokti bhi nahin (wo bhi azab se dochaar ho jaeygi).'' rawahu ibne-Maja, Tirmizi aur Abu-Dawood."
5143,"Hazrat Jarir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''agar koi shakhs kisi qom mein gunah karta ho aur wo log usey rokney ki taqat ke bawajud na roken to phir Allah unke marney se pehley unhen apney azab mein mubtala kar deta hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood w ibne-Maja ."
5144,"Allah Taala ke farman : ''tum apni jaanon ko lazim pakdo , jab tum khud hidayat par hogey to gumrah log tumhen koi nuqsan nahin pahuncha sakengey.'' ke barey mein Abu-Solba (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : sun lo ! Allah ki qism ! maine iskey mutalliq Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se puchha to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''balke tum neki karney ka hukm detey raho aur burai se roktey raho , yahan tak ke jab tum dekho ke bukhl ki itaat ki jati hai, khahish ki ittiba ki jati hai, duniya ko tarjeeh di jati hai aur her shakhs apni raey aur aql par khush hai, aur tum dekho ke eik aisa Amr (baat/kaam) jis se bachna mushkil hai to phir tum apni jaanon ko lazim pakdo aur aam logon ke mamley ko chhod do , kyonkey aagey sabr ke din aaney waley hain, jis shakhs ne un dinon mein sabr kiya goya usney angaara pakda i, un dinon mein amal keiarney waley ke liye pachas aadmiyon ke amal karney ke barabar ajr aur sawab hai.'' Sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! unke pachas aadmiyon ke ajr ki manind? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''un pachas aadmiyon ke ajr ki manind jo tum mein se hain.'' rawahu Tirmizi aur ibne-Maja."
5145,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) namaze-Asr ke baad hamein khutba irshad farmaney ke liye khadey huey to aapney qiyamat tak pesh aaney waley tamam waqiyat bayan farmaai , kuchh logon ne usey yad rakha aur kuchh logon ne usey bhala diya, aap ke khitab mein ye bhi tha, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''duniya sheereen (khushnuma) aur shadab (hari bhari) hai, be-shak Allah tumhen is mein khalifa aur ja-nashin bananey wala hai, wo dekhega ke tum kaisey amal kartey ho, sun lo ! duniya se bacho , aur aurton (ke fitney) se bacho.'' aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne zikr farmaya : ''roze-qiyamat her ehad shikan (todne wale) ke liye , duniya mein uski ehad shikni (todne) ke mutabiq eik jhandaa hoga, aur ameer (sadr) ki ehad shikni (todne) se badh kar koi ehad shikni nahin hogi, uska jhundaa uski peeth par nasab (gaad) kiya jaeyga, aur logon ka khof tum mein se kisi ko haq baat kahney se na rokey jabkey wo usey janta ho.'' eik dusri riwayat mein hai : ''agar wo koi burai dekhey , to usey rok dey logon ka khof usey aisa karney se na rokey.'' chunanche (ye bayan karkey) Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) roney lagey , aur farmaya : yaqinan ham ne usko dekha lekin logon ke khof ne hamein uskey mutalliq baat karney se rok diya, phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''sun lo ! Adam (Alaihissalam) ki aulad mukhtalif tabqo par paida ki gaee , un mein se koi to momin paida kiya gaya, wo usi haalat mein zinda raha aur usi haalat par faut hua , aur un mein se kuchh ko kafir paida kiya gaya, wo haalate-kufr par zinda rahey aur kafir hi faut huye, aur un mein se kuchh momin paida hotey hain, haalate-emaan par zinda rehtey hain aur haalate-kufr par faut ho jatey hain, aur un mein se kuchh haalate-kufr par paida hotey hain, usi haalat par zinda rehtey hain aur haalate-emaan par faut hotey hain.'' aur raawi bayan kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ghussey ka zikr farmaya : ''un mein se kuchh ko jald ghussa aa jata hai aur jald hi utar jata hai, un mein se eik (khaslat) dusri (khaslat) ka badal hai, aur un mein se kuchh aisey hain jinhen ghussa der se aata hai aur der se jata hai ye bhi eik (khaslat) dusri ka badal hai, aur tum mein se behtareen shakhs wo hai jisey ghussa der se aata ho aur jald zaayel (khatam) hota ho, aur tum mein se bad-tareen shakhs wo hai jisey ghussa to jald aata ho jabkey wo zaayel der se hota ho.'' aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ghussey se bacho , kyonkey wo ibne-Adam ke dil par eik angaara hai, kya tum uski ragon ke phoolney aur uski aakhon ki surkhi ki taraf nahin dekhtey, jo shakhs aisi kaifiyat mehsus karey to usey chahiye ke wo let jaey aur zamin ke sath lag jaey.'' raawi bayan kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne qarz ka zikr kiya to farmaya : ''tum mein se koi adaegi mein achchhaa hota hai lekin jab usney kisi se qarz lena ho to wo wasuli mein sakhti karta hai, ye (khaslat) dusri ka badal hai, (taaham (phir bhi) ye wasf (khubi) qabile sataaish (tareef) nahin) kuchh aisey hotey hain ke wo adaegi mein burey hotey hain jabkey wasuli mein achchhey hotey hain to ye bhi dusri (khaslat) ka badal hai, (phir bhi ye khubi qabile tareef nahin) aur tum mein se behtar shakhs wo hai ke jab is par qarz ho to wo achchhi tarah ada karta hai, aur jab usney qarz lena ho to wo wasuli mein achchhaa hota hai, aur tum mein se bad-tareen shakhs wo hai jo qarz ki adaegi mein bura ho aur agar usney qarz lena ho to wo wasuli mein sakht ho.'' yahan tak ke jab dhoop khajoor ke darakhton ki chotiyon aur deewaron ki atraaf par aa gaee to farmaya : ''sun lo ! duniya bas itni hi baqi reh gaee hai jitna aaj ke din ka ye hissey baqi reh gaya hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
5146,"Hazrat Abu-Bakhtari, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke eik sahabi se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''log us waqt tak gunahon ki wajeh se tabah aur barbad nahin kiye jaeyngey jab tak wo gunahon ke jawaz ke liye jhootey uzr pesh nahin karengey.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
5147,"Hazrat Adi bin Adi Kandi bayan kartey hain, hamarey azad karda ghulam ne hamein hadees bayan ki ke usney merey dada ko bayan kartey huey suna unhoney kaha ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''be-shak Allah Taala kuchh logon ki nafarmani ki wajeh se sab logon ko azab mein mubtala nahin karta yahan tak ke wo apney samney burai hoti dekhen aur wo usey rokney ki taqat rakhney ke bawajud usey na roken, jab wo is tarah ke ho jaeyn to phir Allah aam aur khas (ziyada aur thodon sab ko) azab mein mubtala kar deta hai.'' (rawahu fi Sharahus-sunnah)."
5148,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab bani-Israel gunahon mein mubtala ho gaey to unke ulamaa ne unhen mana kiya, wo baaz na aaye to wo (ulamaa) unke ham nasheen aur unke ham niwala w ham piyala bin gaey, Allah ne unke dilon ko eik doosrey ke mushabeh kar diya aur Dawud aur Esa bin Maryam (Alaihissalam) ki zaban par un par lanat farmaey, aur ye isliye hua ke unhoney nafarmani ki aur wo ziyadti kartey they.'' raawi bayan karta hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tek lagaey huey they aur aap beth gaey, phir farmaya : ''nahin (tum bhi kamiyab nahin hogey) us zaat ki qism jiskey haath mein meri jaan hai ! yahan tak ke tum un (gunah gaaron, zalimon) ko sakhti se mana karo.'' aur Abu-Dawood ki riwayat mein hai, farmaya : ''hergiz nahin, Allah ki qism ! tum zarur neki ka hukm karo, tum zarur burai se mana karo aur tum zarur zalim ke haathon ko pakdo tum zarur usey haq ki taraf maael karo aur tum zarur usey haq par qaaim rakho warna phir Allah tumharey dilon ko eik doosrey ke mushabeh kar dega, phir wo tum par bhi lanat farmaeyga jis tarah usney un par lanat farmaee.'' rawahu Tirmizi aur Abu-Dawood."
5149,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''maine Mairaj ki raat kuchh aadmiyon ko dekha ke unke hont aag ki qinchiyon se katrey ja rahey they, maine kaha : Jibrael ! ye kon log hain? unhoney bataya : ye aap ki ummat ke khateeb hazraat hain, ye logon ko to neki ka hukm kartey they magar khud ko bhool jatey they.'' Sharahus-sunnah , Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan , aur unki riwayat mein hai, farmaya : ''aap ki ummat ke wo khateeb hazraat hain jo ye kehtey they wo kartey nahin they, wo Allah ki kitab padhtey they lekin amal nahin kartey they.'' (rawahu fi Sharahus-sunnah aur al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan)."
5150,"Hazrat Ammar bin Yasir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aasman se roti aur gosht par mushtamil dasterkhaan utara gaya aur unhen hukm diya gaya ke wo khayanat na karen aur na kal ke liye zakhira karen, lekin unhoney khayanat ki, zakhira kiya aur kal ke liye utha rakha , jiski wajeh se unhen bandar aur khinzir bana diya gaya.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
5151,"Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aakhiri daur mein meri ummat ko unke baadshaahon ki taraf se masaayib aur mushkilon ka samna karna padeyga , aur un se sirf wohi shakhs bacheyga jo Allah ke Deen ko pehchan kar apni zaban , apney haath aur apney dil ke zariey uskey khilaf jihad karega, ye wo shakhs hai jisey pehli sa'adatein hasil hongi, aur wo shakhs jisney Allah ke Deen ki muaarifat hasil ki aur uski tasdeeq bhi ki, aur wo aadmi jisney Allah ke Deen ko pehchaana lekin us (ke bayan aur tafsil) par khamoshi ikhtiyar ki, agar usney kisi ko achchhaa kaam kartey huey dekha to is par usko pasand kiya, aur agar kisi ko bura kaam kartey huey dekha to is par us se naraz hua. ye shakhs apni makhfi pasand aur napasand par kamiyab ho gaya.'' ( rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan)."
5152,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ne Jibrael (Alaihissalam) ki taraf ""wahi"" farmaee ke falan falan shehar ko uskey baasiyon samet ulat do. usney arz kiya : rab ji ! un main to tera falan banda hai jisney aankh jhapakney ke barabar teri nafarmani nahin ki.'' Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne bayan farmaya : ''Allah taala ne farmaya is (shehar) ko is par aur un par ulat dey, kyonkey uska chehra meri khatir kabhi lamha bhar ke liye bhi mutghaiyar nahin hua.'' ( rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan)."
5153,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' be-shak Allah roze-qiyamat bandey se sawal kartey huey farmaeyga : tujhey kya hua tha ke jab to ne burai dekhi to to ne usey kyon nahin roka? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''usko uski daleel sikha di jaeygi aur wo arz kerega : rab ji ! main logon se dar gaya aur tujh se ummid rakhi.'' Imam Behaqi ne teeno hadisen Shobil-emaan mein naqal ki hain. (rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan)."
5154,"Hazrat Abu-Musa Ash'ari (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''us zaat ki qism jiskey haath mein Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki jaan hai ! be-shak neki aur burai do (alag alag) makhluq hain, roze-qiyamat unhen logon ke samney khada kiya jaeyga, chunanche neki to apney sathiyon (yani nekukaaron) ko khushkhabri deygi aur un se khair ka wada karegi , jabkey burai kahiegi : door raho , door raho , lekin wo (burai karney waley) us se juda nahin ho sakengey.'' (rawahu Ahmed aur al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan)."
